584516,122,214,2,21,1,179,16,"Tattha kiñcāpi {mano}ti avisesena sabbampi catubhūmikacittaṃ vuccati, imasmiṃ pana pade niyamiyamānaṃ vavatthāpiyamānaṃ paricchijjiyamānaṃ aṭṭhavidhaṃ kāmāvacarakusalacittaṃ labbhati. "
