585444,122,398,59,79,1,114,12,"‘ anabhirato, āvuso, brahmacariyaṃ carāmi, na sakkomi brahmacariyaṃ sandhāretuṃ, sikkhaṃ paccakkhāya hīnāyāvattissāmī’’’ ti?"
585445,122,398,80,88,1,14,3,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bhante’’ ti."
585446,122,398,89,112,1,130,15,"‘‘ Kissa pana tvaṃ, nanda, anabhirato brahmacariyaṃ carasi, na sakkosi brahmacariyaṃ sandhāretuṃ, sikkhaṃ paccakkhāya hīnāyāvattissasī’’ ti?"
585447,122,398,113,128,1,104,11,"‘‘ Sākiyānī maṃ, bhante, janapadakalyāṇī gharā nikkhamantassa aḍḍhullikhitehi kesehi apaloketvā maṃ etadavoca–"
585448,122,398,129,162,1,182,22,"‘ tuvaṭaṃ kho, ayyaputta, āgaccheyyāsī’ ti, so kho ahaṃ, bhante, taṃ anussaramāno anabhirato brahmacariyaṃ carāmi, na sakkomi brahmacariyaṃ sandhāretuṃ, sikkhaṃ paccakkhāya hīnāyāvattissāmī’’ ti. "
585449,122,399,2,30,1,296,28,Atha kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ nandaṃ bāhāyaṃ gahetvā iddhibalena tāvatiṃsadevalokaṃ ānento antarāmagge ekasmiṃ jhāmakkhette jhāmakhāṇuke nisinnaṃ chinnakaṇṇanāsanaṅguṭṭhaṃ ekaṃ paluṭṭhamakkaṭiṃ dassetvā tāvatiṃsabhavane sakkassa devarañño upaṭṭhānaṃ āgatāni kakuṭapādāni pañca accharāsatāni dassesi. 
585450,122,399,31,36,1,54,3,{Kakuṭapādānī}ti rattavaṇṇatāya pārevatapādasadisapādāni. 
585451,122,399,37,40,1,18,3,Dassetvā ca panāha–
