586170,122,578,114,123,1,59,8,"Manussā pana aññaṃ hadayena cintenti, aññaṃ mukhena kathenti. "
586171,122,578,124,125,1,8,1,Tenevāha–
586172,122,578,126,153,1,75,9,"‘‘ gahanañhetaṃ, bhante, yadidaṃ manussā, uttānakañhetaṃ, bhante, yadidaṃ pasavo’’ ti( ma. ni.2.3). "
586173,122,579,2,14,1,120,12,Iti so tāya ujucittatāya akuṭilatāya kālaṃ katvā tāvatiṃsabhavane nibbatto accharāsahassaparivuto mahāsampattiṃ anubhosi. 
586174,122,579,15,28,1,132,12,"Tassa kaṇṇamūle mantayantassa saddo soḷasayojanaṭṭhānaṃ pharati, pakatikathāsaddo pana sakalaṃ dasayojanasahassaṃ devanagaraṃ chādeti. "
586175,122,579,29,38,1,41,5,Tenevassa‘‘ ghosakadevaputto’’ ti nāmaṃ ahosi.
586176,122,579,39,47,1,24,4,‘‘ Kissa panesa nissando’’ ti. 
