586178,122,579,53,59,1,30,6,So tattha na ciraṃ ṭhatvā cavi. 
586179,122,579,60,70,1,96,10,Devalokato hi devaputtā āyukkhayena puññakkhayena āhārakkhayena kopenāti catūhi kāraṇehi cavanti. 
586180,122,580,2,16,1,103,13,"Tattha yena bahuṃ puññakammaṃ kataṃ hoti, so devaloke uppajjitvā yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā uparūpari nibbattati. "
586181,122,580,17,21,1,28,4,Evaṃ āyukkhayena cavati nāma. 
586182,122,580,22,42,1,142,17,"Yena parittaṃ puññaṃ kataṃ hoti, tassa rājakoṭṭhāgāre pakkhittaṃ ticatunāḷimattaṃ dhaññaṃ viya antarāva taṃ puññaṃkhīyati, antarāva kālaṃ karoti . "
586183,122,580,43,47,1,30,4,Evaṃ puññakkhayena cavati nāma. 
586184,122,580,48,57,1,92,9,Aparopi kāmaguṇe paribhuñjamāno satisammosena āhāraṃ aparibhuñjitvā kilantakāyo kālaṃ karoti. 
586185,122,580,58,62,1,30,4,Evaṃ āhārakkhayena cavati nāma. 
586186,122,580,63,71,1,57,7,Aparopi parassa sampattiṃ asahanto kujjhitvā kālaṃ karoti. 
586187,122,580,72,76,1,23,4,Evaṃ kopena cavati nāma. 
586188,122,581,2,20,1,140,16,"Ayaṃ pana kāmaguṇe paribhuñjanto muṭṭhassati hutvā āhārakkhayena cavi, cavitvā ca pana kosambiyaṃ nagarasobhiniyā kucchimhi paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. "
586189,122,581,21,42,1,63,11,"Sāpi jātadivase‘‘ kiṃ etan’’ ti dāsiṃ pucchitvā,‘‘ putto, ayye’’ ti vutte–"
586190,122,581,43,59,1,78,10,"‘‘ handa, je, imaṃ dārakaṃ kattarasuppe āropetvā saṅkārakūṭe chaḍḍehī’’ ti chaḍḍāpesi. "
586191,122,581,60,67,1,50,6,"Nagarasobhiniyo hi dhītaraṃ paṭijagganti, na puttaṃ. "
586192,122,581,68,73,1,33,5,Dhītarā hi tāsaṃ paveṇī ghaṭīyati. 
586193,122,581,74,79,1,46,5,Dārakaṃ kākāpi sunakhāpi parivāretvā nisīdiṃsu. 
586194,122,581,80,88,1,82,8,Paccekabuddhe sinehappabhavassa bhukkaraṇassa nissandena ekopi upagantuṃ na visahi. 
586195,122,581,89,123,1,167,25,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe eko manusso bahi nikkhanto taṃ kākasunakhasannipātaṃ disvā,‘‘ kiṃ nu kho etan’’ ti gantvā dārakaṃ disvā puttasinehaṃ paṭilabhitvā‘‘ putto me laddho’’ ti gehaṃ nesi. "
586196,122,581,124,147,1,146,16,"Tadā kosambakaseṭṭhi rājakulaṃ gacchanto rājanivesanato āgacchantaṃ purohitaṃ disvā,‘‘ kiṃ, ācariya, ajja te tithikaraṇanakkhattayogo olokito’’ ti pucchi."
586197,122,581,148,158,1,41,6,"‘‘ Āma, mahāseṭṭhi, amhākaṃ kiṃ aññaṃ kiccanti? "
