586249,122,586,151,159,1,31,4,Kumbhakāro‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
586250,122,586,160,182,1,121,17,"Seṭṭhi punadivase ghosakaṃ pakkositvā,‘‘ hiyyo mayā kumbhakāro ekaṃ kammaṃ āṇatto, ehi, tvaṃ tassa santikaṃ gantvā evaṃ vadehi–"
586251,122,586,183,196,1,56,9,‘ hiyyo kira me pitarā āṇattaṃ kammaṃ nipphādehī’’’ ti pahiṇi. 
586252,122,586,197,205,1,19,4,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti agamāsi. 
586253,122,586,206,245,1,205,28,"Taṃ tattha gacchantaṃ itaro seṭṭhino putto dārakehi saddhiṃ guḷaṃ kīḷanto disvā taṃ pakkositvā,‘‘ kuhiṃ gacchasi bhātikā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ pitu sāsanaṃ gahetvā kumbhakārassa santikan’’ ti vutte‘‘ ahaṃ tattha gamissāmi. "
586254,122,586,246,261,1,67,12,"Ime maṃ dārakā bahuṃ lakkhaṃ jiniṃsu, taṃ me paṭijinitvā dehī’’ ti āha."
586255,122,586,262,270,1,20,4,‘‘ Ahaṃ pitu bhāyāmī’’ ti.
586256,122,586,271,282,1,43,7,"‘‘ Mā bhāyi, bhātika, ahaṃ taṃ sāsanaṃ harissāmi. "
586257,122,586,283,296,1,57,9,"Bahūhi jito, yāvāhaṃ āgacchāmi, tāva me lakkhaṃ paṭijinā’’ ti. "
586258,122,587,2,11,1,52,8,"Ghosako kira guḷakīḷāya cheko, tena naṃ evaṃ nibandhi. "
