586264,122,587,82,121,1,185,27,"Taṃ sutvā seṭṭhi‘‘ ahaṃ dhī’’ ti mahāviravaṃ viravitvā sakalasarīre pakkuthitalohito viya hutvā,‘‘ ambho, kumbhakāra, mā maṃ nāsayi, mā maṃ nāsayī’’ ti bāhā paggayha kandanto tassa santikaṃ agamāsi. "
