586284,122,596,152,172,1,106,15,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti pitaraṃ vanditvā nikkhanto taṃ gāmaṃ patvā seṭṭhissa gharaṃ pucchitvā gantvā seṭṭhijāyaṃ passi.
