586298,122,597,33,49,1,104,12,Seṭṭhidhītāya‘‘ seṭṭhiputto ghosako’’ ti nāmaṃ sutvāva pemaṃ chaviyādīni chinditvā aṭṭhimiñjaṃ āhacca ṭhitaṃ. 
586299,122,597,50,63,1,126,12,"Kotuhalakālasmiñhi sā tassa pajāpatī hutvā nāḷikodanaṃ paccekabuddhassa adāsi, tassānubhāvenāgantvā imasmiṃ seṭṭhikule nibbattā. "
586300,122,597,64,70,1,41,6,Iti taṃ so pubbasineho avattharitvā gaṇhi. 
