586307,122,600,25,34,1,29,5,‘‘ Atthi panassa hatthe kiñcī’’ ti?
586308,122,600,35,43,1,24,4,‘‘ Dussante paṇṇaṃ atthī’’ ti. 
586309,122,600,44,111,1,403,54,"Sā‘‘ kiṃ paṇṇaṃ nu kho etan’’ ti tasmiṃ niddāyante mātāpitūnaṃ aññavihitatāya apassantānaṃ otaritvā samīpaṃ gantvā taṃ paṇṇaṃ mocetvā ādāya attano gabbhaṃ pavisitvā dvāraṃ pidhāya vātapānaṃ vivaritvā akkharasamaye kusalatāya paṇṇaṃ vācetvā,‘‘ aho vata bālo, attano maraṇapaṇṇaṃ dussante bandhitvā vicarati, sace mayā na diṭṭhaṃ assa, natthissa jīvitan’’ ti taṃ paṇṇaṃ phāletvā seṭṭhissa vacanena aparaṃ paṇṇaṃ likhi–"
586310,122,600,112,171,1,410,48,"‘‘ ayaṃ mama putto ghosako nāma, gāmasatato paṇṇākāraṃ āharāpetvā imassa janapadaseṭṭhino dhītarā saddhiṃ maṅgalaṃ katvā attano vasanagāmassa majjhe dvibhūmakaṃ gehaṃ kāretvā pākāraparikkhepena ceva purisaguttiyā ca susaṃvihitārakkhaṃ karotu, mayhañca‘ idañcidañca mayā katan’ ti sāsanaṃ pesetu, evaṃ kate ahaṃ mātulassa kattabbayuttakaṃ pacchā jānissāmī’’ ti, likhitvā ca pana saṅgharitvā otaritvā dussanteyevassa bandhi. "
586311,122,601,2,9,1,52,6,So divasabhāgaṃ niddāyitvā uṭṭhāya bhuñjitvā pakkāmi. 
586312,122,601,10,19,1,74,9,Punadivase pātova taṃ gāmaṃ gantvā āyuttakaṃ gāmakiccaṃ karontaṃyeva passi. 
586313,122,601,20,33,1,31,7,"So taṃ disvā,‘‘ kiṃ, tātā’’ ti pucchi."
586314,122,601,34,44,1,36,6,‘‘ Pitarā me tumhākaṃ paṇṇaṃ pesitan’’ ti.
586315,122,601,45,81,1,162,24,"‘‘ Kiṃ paṇṇaṃ, tāta, āharā’’ ti paṇṇaṃ gahetvā vācetvā tuṭṭhamānaso‘‘ passatha, bho, mama sāmino mayi sinehaṃ katvā jeṭṭhaputtassa me maṅgalaṃ karotū’’ ti mama santikaṃ pahiṇi."
586316,122,601,82,116,1,225,26,‘‘ Sīghaṃ dāruādīni āharathā’’ ti gahapatike vatvā gāmamajjhe vuttapakāraṃ gehaṃ kārāpetvā gāmasatato paṇṇākāraṃ āharāpetvā janapadaseṭṭhino santikā dhītaraṃ ānetvā maṅgalaṃ katvā seṭṭhissa sāsanaṃ pahiṇi‘‘ idañcidañca mayā katan’’ ti. 
586317,122,602,2,13,1,41,8,"Taṃ sutvā seṭṭhino‘‘ yaṃ kāremi, taṃ na hoti; "
586318,122,602,14,26,1,56,9,"yaṃ na kāremi, tadeva hotī’’ ti mahantaṃ domanassaṃ uppajji. "
586319,122,602,27,37,1,77,10,Puttasokena saddhiṃ so soko ekato hutvā kucchiḍāhaṃ uppādetvā atisāraṃ janesi. 
586320,122,602,38,59,1,124,15,"Seṭṭhidhītāpi‘‘ sace koci seṭṭhino santikā āgacchati, mama akathetvā seṭṭhiputtassa paṭhamataraṃ mā kathayitthā’’ ti jane āṇāpesi. "
586321,122,602,60,79,1,104,15,Seṭṭhipi kho‘‘ dāni taṃ duṭṭhaputtaṃ mama sāpateyyassa sāmikaṃ na karissāmī’’ ti cintetvā ekaṃ āyuttakaṃ āha–
586322,122,602,80,97,1,82,11,"‘‘ mātula, puttaṃ me daṭṭhukāmomhi, ekaṃ pādamūlikaṃ pesetvā mama puttaṃ pakkosāpehī’’ ti. "
586323,122,602,98,111,1,50,9,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti vatvā paṇṇaṃ datvā ekaṃ purisaṃ pesesi. 
586324,122,602,112,130,1,87,12,"Seṭṭhidhītāpi tassa āgantvā dvāre ṭhitabhāvaṃ sutvā taṃ pakkosāpetvā,‘‘ kiṃ, tātā’’ ti pucchi. "
586325,122,602,131,133,1,6,2,So āha–
586326,122,602,134,147,1,49,7,"‘‘ seṭṭhi gilāno, puttaṃ passituṃ pakkosāpesi, ayye’’ ti."
586327,122,602,148,160,1,26,5,"‘‘ Kiṃ, tāta, balavā, dubbalo’’ ti?"
586328,122,602,161,173,1,39,6,"‘‘ Balavā tāva, āhāraṃ bhuñjatiyeva, ayye’’ ti. "
586329,122,602,174,193,1,114,14,"Sā seṭṭhiputtaṃ ajānāpetvāva tassa nivesanañca paribbayañca dāpetvā‘‘ mayā pesitakāle gamissasi, acchassu tāvā’’ ti āha. "
586330,122,602,194,214,1,78,13,"Seṭṭhi puna āyuttakaṃ avaca,‘‘ kiṃ, mātula, na te mama puttassa santikaṃ pahitan’’ ti?"
