586343,122,602,343,381,1,132,21,"Seṭṭhidhītā‘‘ idāni gantuṃ kālo’’ ti seṭṭhiputtassa‘‘ pitā te kira gilāno’’ ti ārocetvā‘‘ kiṃ vadesi bhadde’’ ti vutte‘‘ aphāsukamassa, sāmī’’ ti āha."
