586348,122,603,2,32,1,161,24,"Atha naṃ sā‘‘ pitā te dubbalo, ettakaṃ paṇṇākāraṃ gahetvā gacchantānaṃ papañco bhavissati, etaṃ nivattāpehī’’ ti vatvā taṃ sabbaṃ attano kulagehaṃ pesetvā puna taṃ āha–"
586349,122,603,33,49,1,74,10,"‘‘ sāmi, tvaṃ attano pitu pādapasse tiṭṭheyyāsi, ahaṃ ussīsakapasse ṭhassāmī’’ ti. "
586350,122,603,50,68,1,96,14,Gehaṃ pavisamānāyeva ca‘‘ gehassa purato ca pacchato ca ārakkhaṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti attano purise āṇāpesi. 
586351,122,603,69,78,1,72,8,"Paviṭṭhakāle pana seṭṭhiputto pitu pādapasse aṭṭhāsi, itarā ussīsakapasse. "
586352,122,604,2,8,1,41,6,Tasmiṃ khaṇe seṭṭhi uttānako nipanno hoti. 
586353,122,604,9,26,1,64,11,"Āyuttako pana tassa pāde parimajjanto‘‘ putto te, sāmi, āgato’’ ti āha."
586354,122,604,27,34,1,11,3,‘‘ Kuhiṃ so’’ ti?
586355,122,604,35,43,1,21,4,‘‘ Esa pādamūle ṭhito’’ ti. 
586356,122,604,44,60,1,75,11,"Atha naṃ disvā āyakammikaṃ pakkosāpetvā,‘‘ mama gehe kittakaṃ dhanan’’ ti pucchi."
586357,122,604,61,100,1,222,24,"‘‘ Sāmi, dhanasseva cattālīsakoṭiyo, upabhogaparibhogabhaṇḍānaṃ pana vanagāmakkhettadvipadacatuppadayānavāhanānañca ayañca ayañca paricchedo’’ ti vutte,‘‘ ahaṃ ettakaṃ dhanaṃ mama puttassa ghosakassa na demī’’ ti vattukāmo‘‘ demī’’ ti āha. "
586358,122,604,101,159,1,322,45,"Taṃ sutvā seṭṭhidhītā‘‘ ayaṃ puna kathento aññaṃ kiñci katheyyā’’ ti cintetvā sokāturā viya kese vikiritvā rodamānā‘‘ kiṃ nāmetaṃ, tāta, vadetha, idampi nāma vo vacanaṃ suṇoma, alakkhikā vatamhā’’ ti vatvā matthakena naṃ uramajjhe paharantī patitvā yathā puna vattuṃ na sakkoti, tathāssa uramajjhe matthakena ghaṃsentī ārodanaṃ dassesi. "
586359,122,604,160,163,1,31,3,Seṭṭhi taṃkhaṇaññeva kālamakāsi.
586360,122,604,164,177,1,47,7,‘‘ Seṭṭhi mato’’ ti gantvā utenassa rañño ārocayiṃsu. 
586361,122,604,178,195,1,75,12,"Rājā tassa sarīrakiccaṃ kārāpetvā,‘‘ atthi panassa putto vā dhītā vā’’ ti pucchi."
586362,122,604,196,217,1,85,13,"‘‘ Atthi, deva, ghosako nāma tassa putto, sabbaṃ sāpateyyaṃ tassa niyyādetvāva mato, devā’’ ti. "
586363,122,605,2,6,1,40,4,Rājā aparabhāge seṭṭhiputtaṃ pakkosāpesi. 
586364,122,605,7,11,1,26,4,Tasmiñca divase devo vassi. 
586365,122,605,12,17,1,39,5,Rājaṅgaṇe tattha tattha udakaṃ saṇṭhāti. 
586366,122,605,18,27,1,40,5,Seṭṭhiputto‘‘ rājānaṃ passissāmī’’ ti pāyāsi. 
586367,122,605,28,90,1,285,41,"Rājā vātapānaṃ vivaritvā taṃ āgacchantaṃ olokento rājaṅgaṇe udakaṃ laṅghitvā āgacchantaṃ disvā āgantvā vanditvā ṭhitaṃ‘‘ tvaṃ ghosako nāma, tātā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ āma, devā’’ ti vutte‘‘ pitā me matoti mā soci, tava pettikaṃ seṭṭhiṭṭhānaṃ tuyhameva dassāmī’’ ti taṃ samassāsetvā‘‘ gaccha, tātā’’ ti uyyojesi. "
586368,122,605,91,96,1,40,5,Rājā gacchantañca naṃ olokentova aṭṭhāsi. 
586369,122,605,97,105,1,67,8,So āgamanakāle laṅghitaṃ udakaṃ gamanakāle otaritvā saṇikaṃ agamāsi. 
586370,122,605,106,135,1,149,22,"Atha naṃ rājā tatova pakkosāpetvā,‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, tāta, tvaṃ mama santikaṃ āgacchanto udakaṃ laṅghitvā āgamma gacchanto otaritvā saṇikaṃ gacchasī’’ ti pucchi."
586371,122,605,136,157,1,98,15,"‘‘ Āma, deva, ahaṃ tasmiṃ khaṇe kumārako, kīḷanakālo nāma, so idāni pana me devena ṭhānantaraṃ paṭissutaṃ. "
586372,122,605,158,170,1,69,10,Tasmā yathā pure acaritvā idāni sannisinnena hutvā carituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. 
586373,122,605,171,192,1,126,16,"Taṃ sutvā rājā‘‘ dhitimāyaṃ puriso, idānevassa ṭhānantaraṃ dassāmī’’ ti pitarā bhuttaṃ bhogaṃ datvā sabbasatena seṭṭhiṭṭhānaṃ adāsi. "
586374,122,606,2,8,1,41,6,So rathe ṭhatvā nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ akāsi. 
586375,122,606,9,11,1,28,2,Olokitolokitaṭṭhānaṃ kampati. 
586376,122,606,12,34,1,115,16,"Seṭṭhidhītā kāḷidāsiyā saddhiṃ mantayamānā nisinnā ‘‘ amma kāḷi, puttassa te ettikā sampatti maṃ nissāya uppannā’’ ti āha."
586377,122,606,35,44,1,18,4,"‘‘ Kiṃ kāraṇā, ammā’’ ti?"
586378,122,606,45,75,1,191,25,"‘‘ Ayañhi attano maraṇapaṇṇaṃ dussante bandhitvā amhākaṃ gharaṃ āgato, athassa mayā taṃ paṇṇaṃ phāletvā mayā saddhiṃ maṅgalakaraṇatthāya aññaṃ paṇṇaṃ likhitvā ettakaṃ kālaṃ tattha ārakkho kato’’ ti."
586379,122,606,76,102,1,135,19,"‘‘ Amma, tvaṃ ettakaṃ passasi, imaṃ pana seṭṭhi daharakālato paṭṭhāya māretukāmo māretuṃ nāsakkhi, kevalaṃ imaṃ nissāya bahuṃ dhanaṃ khīyī’’ ti."
586380,122,606,103,114,1,39,6,"‘‘ Amma, atibhāriyaṃ vata seṭṭhinā katan’’ ti. "
586381,122,606,115,138,1,115,17,"Nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ katvā gehaṃ pavisantaṃ pana naṃ disvā,‘‘ ayaṃ ettikā sampatti maṃ nissāya uppannā’’ ti hasitaṃ akāsi. "
586382,122,606,139,153,1,52,9,"Atha naṃ seṭṭhiputto disvā,‘‘ kiṃ kāraṇā hasī’’ ti pucchi."
586383,122,606,154,162,1,23,4,‘‘ Ekaṃ kāraṇaṃ nissāyā’’ ti.
586384,122,606,163,170,1,14,3,‘‘ Kathehi nan’’ ti?
586385,122,606,171,178,1,13,3,‘‘ Sā na kathesi’’. 
586386,122,606,179,195,1,71,11,"So‘‘ sace na kathessasi, dvidhā taṃ chindissāmī’’ ti tajjetvā asiṃ nikkaḍḍhi. "
586387,122,606,196,212,1,73,12,Sā‘‘ ayaṃ ettikā sampatti tayā maṃ nissāya laddhāti cintetvā hasitan’’ ti āha.
586388,122,606,213,230,1,73,12,"‘‘ Yadi mama pitarā attano santakaṃ mayhaṃ niyyāditaṃ, tvaṃ ettha kiṃ hosī’’ ti? "
586389,122,606,231,243,1,64,11,"So kira ettakaṃ kālaṃ kiñci na jānāti, tenassā vacanaṃ na saddahi. "
586390,122,606,244,264,1,108,15,"Athassa sā‘‘ tumhākaṃ pitarā maraṇapaṇṇaṃ datvā pesitā, tumhe mayā idañcidañca katvā rakkhitā’’ ti sabbaṃ kathesi."
586391,122,606,265,292,1,91,14,"‘‘ Tvaṃ abhūtaṃ kathesī’’ ti asaddahanto‘‘ mātaraṃ kāḷiṃ pucchissāmī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ evaṃ kira, ammā’’ ti."
586392,122,606,293,328,1,198,26,"‘‘ Āma, tāta, daharakālato paṭṭhāya taṃ māretukāmo māretuṃ asakkonto taṃ nissāya bahuṃ dhanaṃ khīyi, sattasu ṭhānesu tvaṃ maraṇato mutto, idāni bhogagāmato āgamma sabbasatena saddhiṃ seṭṭhiṭṭhānaṃ patto’’ ti. "
586393,122,606,329,361,1,201,25,"So taṃ sutvā‘‘ bhāriyaṃ vata kammaṃ, evarūpā kho pana maraṇā muttassa mama pamādajīvitaṃ jīvituṃ ayuttaṃ, appamatto bhavissāmī’’ ti cintetvā devasikaṃ sahassaṃ vissajjetvā addhikakapaṇādīnaṃ dānaṃ paṭṭhapesi. "
