586402,122,607,76,103,1,175,23,"Tesu ye bhittiṃ bhinditvā palāyanti, te jīvitaṃ labhanti, tadā pana seṭṭhi ca bhariyā ca dhītā cassa tathā palāyitvā ghosakaseṭṭhiṃ passituṃ patthentā kosambimaggaṃ paṭipajjiṃsu. "
