586976,122,689,18,22,1,28,4,Ke panetaṃ visesaṃ jānantīti? 
586977,122,689,23,40,1,124,15,"Appamādamhi {paṇḍitā}ti ye paṇḍitā medhāvino sappaññā attano appamāde ṭhatvā appamādaṃ vaḍḍhenti, te evaṃ visesakāraṇaṃ jānanti. "
586978,122,689,41,55,1,103,12,"Appamāde {pamodantī}ti te evaṃ ñatvā tasmiṃ attano appamāde pamodanti, pahaṃsitamukhā tuṭṭhapahaṭṭhā honti. "
586979,122,689,56,81,1,250,23,"Ariyānaṃ gocare {ratā}ti te evaṃ appamāde pamodantā taṃ appamādaṃ vaḍḍhetvā ariyānaṃ buddhapaccekabuddhabuddhasāvakānaṃ gocarasaṅkhāte catusatipaṭṭhānādibhede sattatiṃsa bodhipakkhiyadhamme navavidhalokuttaradhamme ca ratā niratā, abhiratā hontīti attho. "
586980,122,690,2,17,1,163,13,Te {jhāyino}ti te appamattā paṇḍitā aṭṭhasamāpattisaṅkhātena ārammaṇūpanijjhānena vipassanāmaggaphalasaṅkhātena lakkhaṇūpanijjhānena cāti duvidhenapi jhānena jhāyino. 
586981,122,690,18,26,1,95,7,{Sātatikā}ti abhinikkhamanakālato paṭṭhāya yāva arahattamaggā satataṃ pavattakāyikacetasikavīriyā. 
586982,122,690,27,50,1,222,21,"Niccaṃ {daḷhaparakkamā}ti yaṃ taṃ purisathāmena purisavīriyena purisaparakkamena pattabbaṃ, na taṃ apāpuṇitvā vīriyassa saṇṭhānaṃ bhavissatīti evarūpena vīriyena antarā anosakkitvā niccappavattena daḷhaparakkamena samannāgatā. "
586983,122,690,51,61,1,60,8,"{Phusantī}ti ettha dve phusanā ñāṇaphusanā ca, vipākaphusanā ca. "
586984,122,690,62,72,1,72,9,"Tattha cattāro maggā ñāṇaphusanā nāma, cattāri phalāni vipākaphusanā nāma. "
586985,122,690,73,77,1,33,4,Tesu idha vipākaphusanā adhippetā. 
586986,122,690,78,90,1,102,10,"Ariyaphalena nibbānaṃ sacchikaronto dhīrā paṇḍitā tāya vipākaphusanāya phusanti, nibbānaṃ sacchikaronti. "
586987,122,690,91,108,1,143,16,"Yogakkhemaṃ anuttaran ti ye cattāro yogā mahājanaṃ vaṭṭe osīdāpenti, tehi khemaṃ nibbhayaṃ sabbehi lokiyalokuttaradhammehi seṭṭhattā anuttaranti. "
