586991,122,693,2,4,1,25,2,2 . Kumbhaghosakaseṭṭhivatthu 
586992,122,694,2,13,1,89,9,{Uṭṭhānavato}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto kumbhaghosakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
586993,122,694,14,44,1,231,26,"Rājagahanagarasmiñhi rājagahaseṭṭhino gehe ahivātarogo uppajji, tasmiṃ uppanne makkhikā ādiṃ katvā yāva gāvā paṭhamaṃ tiracchānagatā maranti, tato dāsakammakaro, sabbapacchā gehasāmikā, tasmā so rogo sabbapacchā seṭṭhiñca jāyañca gaṇhi. "
586994,122,694,45,56,1,79,11,Te rogena phuṭṭhā puttaṃ santike ṭhitaṃ oloketvā assupuṇṇehi nettehi taṃ āhaṃsu–
586995,122,694,57,93,1,228,28,"‘‘ tāta, imasmiṃ kira roge uppanne bhittiṃ bhinditvā palāyantāva jīvitaṃ labhanti, tvaṃ amhe anoloketvā palāyitvā jīvanto punāgantvā amhākaṃ asukaṭṭhāne nāma cattālīsa dhanakoṭiyo nidahitvā ṭhapitā, tā uddharitvā jīvikaṃ kappeyyāsī’’ ti. "
586996,122,694,94,114,1,183,19,So tesaṃ vacanaṃ sutvā rudamāno mātāpitaro vanditvā maraṇabhayabhīto bhittiṃ bhinditvā palāyitvā pabbatagahanaṃ gantvā dvādasa vassāni tattha vasitvā mātāpituvasanaṭṭhānaṃ paccāgañchi. 
586997,122,695,2,11,1,72,9,Atha naṃ daharakāle gantvā parūḷhakesamassukāle āgatattā na koci sañjāni. 
586998,122,695,12,21,1,85,9,So mātāpitūhi dinnasaññāvasena dhanaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā dhanassa arogabhāvaṃ ñatvā cintesi–
586999,122,695,22,52,1,153,21,"‘‘ maṃ na koci sañjānāti, sacāhaṃ dhanaṃ uddharitvā valañjissāmi,‘ ekena duggatena nidhi uddhaṭo’ ti maṃ gahetvā viheṭheyyuṃ, yaṃnūnāhaṃ bhatiṃ katvā jīveyyan’’ ti. "
587000,122,695,53,69,1,90,11,"Athekaṃ pilotikaṃ nivāsetvā,‘‘ atthi koci bhatakena atthiko’’ ti pucchanto bhatakavīthiṃ pāpuṇi. "
587001,122,695,70,90,1,92,14,"Atha naṃ bhatakā disvā,‘‘ sace amhākaṃ ekaṃ kammaṃ karissasi, bhattavetanaṃ te dassāmā’’ ti āhaṃsu."
587002,122,695,91,99,1,18,4,‘‘ Kiṃ kammaṃ nāmā’’ ti?
587003,122,695,100,103,1,21,1,‘‘ Pabodhanacodanakammaṃ. 
587004,122,695,104,123,1,114,13,"Sace ussahasi, pātova uṭṭhāya‘ tātā, uṭṭhahatha, sakaṭāni sannayhatha, goṇe yojetha, hatthiassānaṃ tiṇatthāya gamanavelā; "
587005,122,695,124,141,1,77,11,"ammā, tumhepi uṭṭhahatha, yāguṃ pacatha, bhattaṃ pacathā’ ti vicaritvā ārocehī’’ ti. "
587006,122,695,142,150,1,23,4,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
587007,122,695,151,156,1,39,5,Athassa vasanatthāya ekaṃ gharaṃ adaṃsu. 
587008,122,695,157,162,1,29,5,So devasikaṃ taṃ kammaṃ akāsi. 
587009,122,696,2,7,1,46,5,Athassa ekadivasaṃ rājā bimbisāro saddamassosi. 
587010,122,696,8,12,1,26,4,So pana sabbaravaññū ahosi. 
587011,122,696,13,23,1,43,6,Tasmā‘‘ mahādhanassa purisassesa saddo’’ ti āha. 
587012,122,696,24,48,1,105,18,"Athassa santike ṭhitā ekā paricārikā‘‘ rājā yaṃ vā taṃ vā na kathessati, idaṃ mayā ñātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti cintetvā–"
587013,122,696,49,63,1,46,8,"‘‘ gaccha, tāta, etaṃ jānāhī’’ ti ekaṃ purisaṃ pahiṇi. "
587014,122,696,64,82,1,90,13,"So vegena gantvā taṃ disvā āgantvā,‘‘ eko bhatakānaṃ bhatikārako kapaṇamanusso eso’’ ti ārocesi. "
587015,122,696,83,97,1,101,14,Rājā tassa vacanaṃ sutvā tuṇhī hutvā dutiyadivasepi tatiyadivasepi taṃ tassa saddaṃ sutvā tatheva āha. 
587016,122,696,98,115,1,86,11,"Sāpi paricārikā tatheva cintetvā punappunaṃ pesetvā,‘‘ kapaṇamanusso eso’’ ti vutte cintesi–"
587017,122,696,116,148,1,169,21,"‘‘ rājā‘ kapaṇamanusso eso’ ti vacanaṃ sutvāpi na saddahati, punappunaṃ‘ mahādhanassa purisassesa saddo’ ti vadati, bhavitabbamettha kāraṇena, yathāsabhāvato etaṃ ñātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
587018,122,696,149,171,1,102,15,"Sā rājānaṃ āha,‘‘ deva , ahaṃ sahassaṃ labhamānā dhītaraṃ ādāya gantvā etaṃ dhanaṃ rājakulaṃ pavesessāmī’’ ti. "
587019,122,696,172,176,1,26,4,Rājā tassā sahassaṃ dāpesi. 
587020,122,697,2,37,1,233,28,"Sā taṃ gahetvā dhītaraṃ ekaṃ malinadhātukaṃ vatthaṃ nivāsāpetvā tāya saddhiṃ rājagehato nikkhamitvā maggapaṭipannā viya bhatakavīthiṃ gantvā ekaṃ gharaṃ pavisitvā,‘‘ amma, mayaṃ maggapaṭipannā, ekāhadvīhaṃ idha vissamitvā gamissāmā’’ ti āha."
587021,122,697,38,60,1,105,14,"‘‘ Amma, bahūni gharamānusakāni, na sakkā idha vasituṃ, etaṃ kumbhaghosakassa gehaṃ tucchaṃ, tattha gacchathā’’ ti. "
587022,122,697,61,97,1,183,23,"Sā tattha gantvā,‘‘ sāmi, mayaṃ maggapaṭipannakā, ekāhadvīhaṃ idha vasissāmā’’ ti vatvā tena punappunaṃ paṭikkhittāpi,‘‘ sāmi, ajjekadivasamattaṃ vasitvā pātova gamissāmā’’ ti nikkhamituṃ na icchi. "
587023,122,697,98,163,1,404,49,"Sā tattheva vasitvā punadivase tassa araññagamanavelāya,‘‘ sāmi, tava nivāpaṃ datvā yāhi , āhāraṃ te pacissāmī’’ ti vatvā,‘‘ alaṃ, amma, ahameva pacitvā bhuñjissāmī’’ ti vutte punappunaṃ nibandhitvā tena dinne gahitamattakeyeva katvā antarāpaṇato bhājanāni ceva parisuddhataṇḍulādīni ca āharāpetvā rājakule pacananiyāmena suparisuddhaṃ odanaṃ, sādhurasāni ca dve tīṇi sūpabyañjanāni pacitvā tassa araññato āgatassa adāsi. "
587024,122,697,164,184,1,92,13,"Atha naṃ bhuñjitvā muducittataṃ āpannaṃ ñatvā,‘‘ sāmi, kilantamha, ekāhadvīhaṃ idheva homā’’ ti āha. "
587025,122,697,185,193,1,23,4,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
587026,122,698,2,8,1,57,6,Athassa sāyampi punadivasepi madhurabhattaṃ pacitvā adāsi. 
587027,122,698,9,23,1,64,9,"Atha muducittataṃ tassa ñatvā‘‘ sāmi, katipāhaṃ idheva vasissāmā’’ ti. "
587028,122,698,24,34,1,85,10,Tattha vasamānā tikhiṇena satthena tassa mañcavāṇaṃ heṭṭhāaṭaniyaṃ tahaṃ tahaṃ chindi. 
587029,122,698,35,41,1,51,6,Mañco tasmiṃ āgantvā nisinnamatteyeva heṭṭhā olambi. 
587030,122,698,42,55,1,46,9,So‘‘ kasmā ayaṃ mañco evaṃ chijjitvā gato’’ ti āha.
587031,122,698,56,70,1,60,8,"‘‘ Sāmi, daharadārake vāretuṃ na sakkomi, ettheva sannipatantī’’ ti."
587032,122,698,71,81,1,40,7,"‘‘ Amma, idaṃ me dukkhaṃ tumhe nissāya jātaṃ. "
587033,122,698,82,92,1,60,8,Ahañhi pubbe katthaci gacchanto dvāraṃ pidahitvā gacchāmī’’ ti.
587034,122,698,93,106,1,37,7,"‘‘ Kiṃ karomi, tāta, vāretuṃ na sakkomī’’ ti. "
587035,122,698,107,127,1,139,20,Sā imināva niyāmena dve tayo divase chinditvā tena ujjhāyitvā khīyitvā vuccamānāpi tatheva vatvā puna ekaṃ dve rajjuke ṭhapetvā sese chindi. 
587036,122,698,128,167,1,198,27,"Taṃ divasaṃ tasmiṃ nisinnamatteyeva sabbaṃ vāṇaṃ bhūmiyaṃ pati, sīsaṃ jaṇṇukehi saddhiṃ ekato ahosi, so uṭṭhāya,‘‘ kiṃ karomi, idāni kuhiṃ gamissāmi , nipajjanamañcassapi tumhehi asāmiko viya katomhī’’ ti āha."
587037,122,698,168,208,1,174,25,"‘‘ Tāta, kiṃ karomi, paṭivissakadārake vāretuṃ na sakkomi, hotu, mā cintayi, imāya nāma velāya kuhiṃ gamissasī’’ ti dhītaraṃ āmantetvā,‘‘ amma, tava bhātikassa nipajjanokāsaṃ karohī’’ ti āha. "
587038,122,698,209,221,1,42,7,"Sā ekapasse sayitvā‘‘ idhāgaccha, sāmī’’ ti āha. "
587039,122,698,222,237,1,59,9,"Itaropi naṃ‘‘ gaccha, tāta, bhaginiyā saddhiṃ nipajjā’’ ti vadesi. "
