587379,122,787,2,4,1,11,2,7 . Maghavatthu 
587380,122,788,2,16,1,128,13,Appamādena {maghavā}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā vesāliyaṃ upanissāya kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ viharanto sakkaṃ devarājānaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
587381,122,789,2,38,1,173,20,"Vesāliyañhi mahāli nāma licchavī vasati, so tathāgatassa sakkapañhasuttantadesanaṃ( dī. ni.2.344 ādayo) sutvā‘‘ sammāsambuddho sakkasampattiṃ mahatiṃ katvā kathesi,‘ disvā nu kho kathesi, udāhu adisvā. "
587382,122,789,39,54,1,59,11,"Jānāti nu kho sakkaṃ, udāhu no’ ti pucchissāmi nan’’ ti cintesi. "
587383,122,789,55,80,1,166,19,"Atha kho, mahāli, licchavī yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami, upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi, ekamantaṃ nisinno kho, mahāli, licchavī bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–"
587384,122,789,81,95,1,48,7,"‘‘ diṭṭho kho, bhante, bhagavatā sakko devānamindo’’ ti?"
587385,122,789,96,110,1,41,7,"‘‘ Diṭṭho kho me , mahāli, sakko devānamindo’’ ti."
587386,122,789,111,122,1,44,6,"‘‘ So hi nuna, bhante, sakkapatirūpako bhavissati . "
587387,122,789,123,133,1,38,6,"Duddaso hi, bhante, sakko devānamindo’’ ti."
587388,122,789,134,157,1,122,15,"‘‘ Sakkañca khvāhaṃ, mahāli, pajānāmi sakkakaraṇe ca dhamme, yesaṃ dhammānaṃ samādinnattā sakko sakkattaṃ ajjhagā, tañca pajānāmi’’. "
587389,122,790,2,23,1,99,14,"Sakko , mahāli, devānamindo pubbe manussabhūto samāno magho nāma māṇavo ahosi, tasmā‘‘ maghavā’’ ti vuccati. "
587390,122,791,2,22,1,94,13,"Sakko , mahāli, devānamindo pubbe manussabhūto samāno pure dānaṃ adāsi, tasmā‘‘ purindado’’ ti vuccati. "
587391,122,792,2,22,1,95,13,"Sakko , mahāli, devānamindo pubbe manussabhūto samāno sakkaccaṃ dānaṃ adāsi, tasmā‘‘ sakko’’ ti vuccati. "
587392,122,793,2,21,1,90,12,"Sakko , mahāli, devānamindo pubbe manussabhūto samāno āvasathaṃ adāsi, tasmā‘‘ vāsavo’’ ti vuccati. "
587393,122,794,2,20,1,89,11,"Sakko , mahāli, devānamindo sahassampi atthaṃ muhuttena cinteti, tasmā‘‘ sahassakkho’’ ti vuccati. "
587394,122,795,2,21,1,87,11,"Sakkassa , mahāli, devānamindassa sujā nāma asurakaññā, pajāpati, tasmā‘‘ sujampatī’’ ti vuccati. "
587395,122,796,2,21,1,106,12,"Sakko , mahāli, devānamindo devānaṃ tāvatiṃsānaṃ issariyādhipaccaṃ rajjaṃ kāreti, tasmā‘‘ devānamindo’’ ti vuccati. "
587396,122,797,2,21,1,141,15,"Sakkassa , mahāli, devānamindassa pubbe manussabhūtassa satta vatapadāni samattāni samādinnāni ahesuṃ, yesaṃ samādinnattā sakko sakkattaṃ ajjhagā. "
587397,122,797,22,25,1,25,3,Katamāni satta vatapadāni? 
587398,122,797,26,55,1,244,24,"Yāvajīvaṃ mātāpettibharo assaṃ, yāvajīvaṃ kule jeṭṭhāpacāyī assaṃ, yāvajīvaṃ saṇhavāco assaṃ, yāvajīvaṃ apisuṇavāco assaṃ, yāvajīvaṃ vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvaseyyaṃ, muttacāgo payatapāṇi vosaggarato yācayogo dānasaṃvibhāgarato assaṃ. "
587399,122,797,56,78,1,108,14,"Yāvajīvaṃ saccavāco assaṃ, yāvajīvaṃ akkodhano assaṃ,‘‘ sacepi me kodho uppajjeyya, khippameva na paṭivineyyan’’ ti. "
587400,122,797,79,99,1,149,16,"Sakkassa, mahāli, devānamindassa pubbe manussabhūtassa imāni satta vatapadāni samattāni samādinnāni ahesuṃ, yesaṃ samādinnattā sakko sakkattaṃ ajjhagāti."
587401,122,798,2,9,1,43,5,"‘ ‘ Mātāpettibharaṃ jantuṃ, kule jeṭṭhāpacāyinaṃ; "
587402,122,799,2,6,1,43,3,"Saṇhaṃ sakhilasambhāsaṃ, pesuṇeyyappahāyinaṃ."
587403,122,800,2,10,1,47,6,"‘ ‘ Maccheravinaye yuttaṃ, saccaṃ kodhābhibhuṃ naraṃ; "
587404,122,801,2,23,1,42,8,"Taṃ ve devā tāvatiṃsā, āhu sappuriso itī’’ ti.( saṃ. ni.1.257)– "
587405,122,802,2,23,1,103,13,"Idaṃ , mahāli, sakkena maghamāṇavakāle katakammanti vatvā puna tena‘‘ kathaṃ, bhante, maghamāṇavo paṭipajjī’’ ti? "
587406,122,802,24,43,1,89,13,"Tassa paṭipattiṃ vitthārato sotukāmena puṭṭho‘‘ tena hi, mahāli, suṇāhī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari– "
587407,122,803,2,19,1,149,16,Atīte magadharaṭṭhe macalagāme magho nāma māṇavo gāmakammakaraṇaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā attano ṭhitaṭṭhānaṃ pādantena paṃsuṃ viyūhitvā ramaṇīyaṃ katvā aṭṭhāsi. 
587408,122,803,20,29,1,61,9,Aparo taṃ bāhunā paharitvā tato apanetvā sayaṃ tattha aṭṭhāsi. 
587409,122,803,30,38,1,56,8,So tassa akujjhitvāva aññaṃ ṭhānaṃ ramaṇīyaṃ katvā ṭhito. 
587410,122,803,39,48,1,63,9,Tatopi naṃ añño āgantvā bāhunā paharitvā apanetvā sayaṃ aṭṭhāsi. 
587411,122,803,49,68,1,145,18,"So tassapi akujjhitvāva aññaṃ ṭhānaṃ ramaṇīyaṃ katvā ṭhito, iti taṃ gehato nikkhantā nikkhantā purisā bāhunā paharitvā ṭhitaṭhitaṭṭhānato apanesuṃ. "
587412,122,803,69,96,1,176,21,"So‘‘ sabbepete maṃ nissāya sukhitā jātā, iminā kammena mayhaṃ sukhadāyakena puññakammena bhavitabban’’ ti cintetvā, punadivase kudālaṃ ādāya khalamaṇḍalamattaṃ ṭhānaṃ ramaṇīyaṃ akāsi. "
587413,122,803,97,101,1,30,4,Sabbe gantvā tattheva aṭṭhaṃsu. 
587414,122,803,102,111,1,56,8,"Atha nesaṃ sītasamaye aggiṃ katvā adāsi, gimhakāle udakaṃ. "
587415,122,803,112,151,1,236,30,"Tato‘‘ ramaṇīyaṃ ṭhānaṃ nāma sabbesaṃ piyaṃ, kassaci appiyaṃ nāma natthi, ito paṭṭhāya mayā maggaṃ samaṃ karontena vicarituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti cintetvā, pātova nikkhamitvā, maggaṃ samaṃ karonto chinditvā, haritabbayuttakā rukkhasākhā haranto vicarati. "
