587637,122,836,2,4,1,27,2,9 . Nigamavāsitissattheravatthu 
587638,122,837,2,13,1,103,10,{Appamādarato}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto nigamavāsitissattheraṃ nāma ārabbha kathesi. 
587639,122,838,2,25,1,189,19,Ekasmiñhi sāvatthito avidūre nigamagāme jātasaṃvaḍḍho eko kulaputto satthu sāsane pabbajitvā laddhūpasampado‘‘ nigamavāsitissatthero nāma appiccho santuṭṭho pavivitto āraddhavīriyo’’ ti paññāyi. 
587640,122,838,26,31,1,42,5,So nibaddhaṃ ñātigāmeyeva piṇḍāya vicarati. 
587641,122,838,32,42,1,97,8,"Anāthapiṇḍikādīsu mahādānāni karontesu, pasenadikosale asadisadānaṃ karontepi sāvatthiṃ nāgacchati. "
587642,122,838,43,70,1,212,20,"Bhikkhū‘‘ ayaṃ nigamavāsitissatthero uṭṭhāya samuṭṭhāya ñātisaṃsaṭṭho viharati, anāthapiṇḍikādīsu mahādānādīni karontesu, pasenadikosale asadisadānaṃ karontepi neva āgacchatī’’ ti kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpetvā satthu ārocayiṃsu. "
587643,122,838,71,110,1,186,26,"Satthā taṃ pakkosāpetvā,‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, bhikkhu, evaṃ karosī’’ ti pucchitvā,‘‘ natthi, bhante, mayhaṃ ñātisaṃsaggo, ahaṃ ete manusse nissāya ajjhoharaṇīyamattaṃ āhāraṃ labhāmi lūkhe vā paṇīte vā. "
587644,122,838,111,136,1,156,21,"Yāpanamatte laddhe puna kiṃ āhārapariyesanenāti na gacchāmi, ñātīhi pana me saṃsaggo nāma natthi, bhante’’ ti vutte satthā pakatiyāpi tassa ajjhāsayaṃ vijānanto–"
587645,122,838,137,164,1,128,18,"‘‘ sādhu sādhu, bhikkhū’’ ti tassa sādhukāraṃ datvā,‘‘ anacchariyaṃ kho panetaṃ bhikkhu, yaṃ tvaṃ mādisaṃ ācariyaṃ labhitvā appiccho ahosi. "
587646,122,838,165,181,1,84,13,"Ayañhi appicchatā nāma mama tanti, mama paveṇī’’ ti vatvā bhikkhūhi yācito atītaṃ āhari– "
587647,122,839,2,10,1,72,8,Atīte himavante gaṅgātīre ekasmiṃ udumbaravane anekasahassā suvā vasiṃsu. 
587648,122,839,11,41,1,203,28,"Tatreko suvarājā attano nivāsarukkhassa phalesu khīṇesu yaṃ yadeva avasiṭṭhaṃ hoti aṅkuro vā pattaṃ vā taco vā, taṃ taṃ khāditvā gaṅgāyaṃ pānīyaṃ pivitvā paramappiccho santuṭṭho hutvā aññattha na gacchati. "
587649,122,839,42,47,1,58,5,Tassa appicchasantuṭṭhabhāvaguṇena sakkassa bhavanaṃ kampi. 
587650,122,839,48,59,1,88,11,Sakko āvajjamāno taṃ disvā tassa vīmaṃsanatthaṃ attano ānubhāvena taṃ rukkhaṃ sukkhāpesi. 
