587747,122,871,145,169,1,133,17,"‘‘ ayaṃ upāsikā mayā sabbaṃ cintitacintitaṃ pesesi, ahaṃ etaṃ daṭṭhukāmo, aho vata me nānaggarasabhojanaṃ gāhāpetvā sayameva āgaccheyyā’’ ti. "
587748,122,871,170,190,1,106,15,"Upāsikā‘‘ mama putto maṃ daṭṭhukāmo, āgamanaṃ me paccāsīsatī’’ ti bhojanaṃ gāhāpetvā vihāraṃ gantvā tassa adāsi. "
587749,122,871,191,204,1,61,8,"So katabhattakicco‘‘ mātikamātā nāma tvaṃ, mahāupāsike’’ ti pucchi."
587750,122,871,205,213,1,11,3,"‘‘ Āma, tātā’’ ti."
587751,122,871,214,222,1,25,4,‘‘ Tvaṃ paracittaṃ jānāsī’’ ti?
587752,122,871,223,233,1,24,5,"‘‘ Kiṃ maṃ pucchasi, tātā’’ ti?"
587753,122,871,234,246,1,53,7,"‘‘ Mayā cintitacintitaṃ sabbamakāsi, tena taṃ pucchāmī’’ ti."
587754,122,871,247,256,1,37,4,"‘‘ Paracittajānanakabhikkhū bahū, tātā’’ ti?"
587755,122,871,257,270,1,45,7,"‘‘ Nāhaṃ aññe pucchāmi, tuvaṃ pucchāmi, upāsike’’ ti. "
587756,122,871,271,294,1,98,15,Evaṃ santepi upāsikā‘‘ paracittaṃ jānāmī’’ ti avatvā‘‘ paracittaṃ jānantā nāma evaṃ karonti puttā’’ ti āha. 
587757,122,871,295,342,1,244,33,"So‘‘ bhāriyaṃ vatidaṃ kammaṃ, puthujjanā nāma sobhanampi asobhanampi cintenti, sacāhaṃ kiñci ayuttaṃ cintayissāmi, saha bhaṇḍakena coraṃ cūḷāya gaṇhantī viya maṃ vippakāraṃ pāpeyya, mayā ito palāyituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti cintetvā,‘‘ upāsike, ahaṃ gamissāmī’’ ti āha."
587758,122,871,343,351,1,13,3,"‘‘ Kahaṃ, ayyā’’ ti?"
587759,122,871,352,361,1,26,4,"‘‘ Satthu santikaṃ, upāsike’’ ti."
587760,122,871,362,373,1,27,5,"‘‘ Vasatha tāva, bhante, idhā’’ ti."
587761,122,871,374,389,1,71,9,"‘‘ Na vasissāmi, upāsike, gamissāmevā’’ ti nikkhamitvā satthu santikaṃ agamāsi. "
587762,122,871,390,405,1,59,11,Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ kiṃ bhikkhu na tvaṃ tattha vasasī’’ ti pucchi.
587763,122,871,406,419,1,37,7,"‘‘ Āma, bhante, na sakkā tattha vasitun’’ ti."
587764,122,871,420,428,1,21,4,‘‘ Kiṃ kāraṇā bhikkhū’’ ti?
587765,122,871,429,466,1,222,28,"‘‘ Bhante, sā upāsikā cintitacintitaṃ sabbaṃ jānāti, puthujjanā ca nāma sobhanampi asobhanampi cintenti, sacāhaṃ kiñci ayuttaṃ cintessāmi, saha bhaṇḍakena coraṃ cūḷāya gaṇhantī viya maṃ vippakāraṃ pāpessatī’’ ti cintetvā āgatomhīti."
587766,122,871,467,493,1,84,13,"‘‘ Bhikkhu, tattheva tayā vasituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti ,‘‘ na sakkomi, bhante, nāhaṃ tattha vasissāmī’’ ti."
587767,122,871,494,508,1,53,8,"‘‘ Tena hi tvaṃ, bhikkhu, ekameva rakkhituṃ sakkhissasī’’ ti."
587768,122,871,509,517,1,13,3,"‘‘ Kiṃ, bhante’’ ti?"
587769,122,871,518,547,1,151,21,"‘‘ Tava cittameva rakkha, cittaṃ nāmetaṃ durakkhaṃ, tvaṃ attano cittameva niggaṇha, mā aññaṃ kiñci cintayi, cittaṃ nāmetaṃ dunniggahan’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
587770,122,872,2,4,1,0,0,35.
587771,122,873,2,8,1,39,4,"‘ ‘ Dunniggahassa lahuno, yatthakāmanipātino; "
587772,122,874,2,12,1,50,7,"Cittassa damatho sādhu, cittaṃ dantaṃ sukhāvahan’’ ti. "
587773,122,875,2,8,1,55,6,Tattha cittaṃ nāmetaṃ dukkhena niggayhatīti dunniggahaṃ. 
587774,122,875,9,15,1,39,6,Lahuṃ uppajjati ca nirujjhati cāti lahu. 
587775,122,875,16,19,1,26,3,Tassa dunniggahassa lahuno. 
587776,122,875,20,25,1,56,4,{Yatthakāmanipātino}ti yattha katthacideva nipatanasīlassa. 
587777,122,875,26,48,1,130,18,"Etañhi labhitabbaṭṭhānaṃ vā alabhitabbaṭṭhānaṃ vā yuttaṭṭhānaṃ vā ayuttaṭṭhānaṃ vā na jānāti, neva jātiṃ oloketi, na gottaṃ, na vayaṃ. "
587778,122,875,49,63,1,76,9,"Yattha yattha icchati, tattha tattheva nipatatīti‘‘ yatthakāmanipātī’’ ti vuccati. "
587779,122,875,64,79,1,116,14,"Tassa evarūpassa cittassa damatho sādhu catūhi ariyamaggehi dantabhāvo yathā nibbisevanaṃ hoti, tathā katabhāvo sādhu. "
587780,122,875,80,82,1,10,2,Kiṃ kāraṇā? 
587781,122,875,83,92,1,103,9,Idañhi cittaṃ dantaṃ sukhāvahaṃ nibbisevanaṃ kataṃ maggaphalasukhaṃ paramatthanibbānasukhañca āvahatīti. 
587782,122,876,2,12,1,100,9,"Desanāpariyosāne sampattaparisāya bahū sotāpannādayo ahesuṃ, mahājanassa sātthikā dhammadesanā jātāti. "
587783,122,877,2,25,1,105,15,"Satthā tassa bhikkhuno imaṃ ovādaṃ datvā,‘‘ gaccha, bhikkhu, aññaṃ kiñci acintayitvā tattheva vasāhī’’ ti pahiṇi. "
587784,122,877,26,34,1,56,8,So bhikkhu satthu santikā ovādaṃ labhitvā tattha agamāsi. 
587785,122,877,35,41,1,39,6,Kiñci bahiddhā cintanaṃ nāma na cintesi. 
587786,122,877,42,68,1,180,21,"Mahāupāsikāpi dibbena cakkhunā olokentī theraṃ disvā,‘‘ idāni ovādadāyakaṃ ācariyaṃ labhitvā punāgato mama putto’’ ti attano ñāṇeneva paricchinditvā tassa sappāyāhāraṃ paṭiyādetvā adāsi. "
587787,122,877,69,121,1,340,40,"So sappāyabhojanaṃ sevitvā katipāheneva arahattaṃ patvā maggaphalasukhena vītināmento‘‘ aho mahāupāsikā mayhaṃ patiṭṭhā jātā, ahaṃ imaṃ nissāya bhavanissaraṇaṃ pattomhī’’ ti cintetvā,‘‘ imasmiṃ tāva me attabhāve patiṭṭhā jātā, saṃsāre pana me saṃsarantassa aññesupi attabhāvesu ayaṃ patiṭṭhā bhūtapubbā, no’’ ti upadhārento ekūnaattabhāvasataṃ anussari. "
587788,122,877,122,132,1,93,10,Sāpi ekūnaattabhāvasate tassa pādaparicārikā aññesu paṭibaddhacittā hutvā taṃ jīvitā voropesi. 
587789,122,877,133,152,1,87,13,"Thero tassā ettakaṃ aguṇaṃ disvā,‘‘ aho mayaṃ mahāupāsikā bhāriyaṃ kammaṃ akāsī’’ ti cintesi. "
587790,122,878,2,95,1,490,68,"Mahāupāsikāpi gehe nisinnāva‘‘ kiṃ nu kho mayhaṃ puttassa pabbajitakiccaṃ mattakaṃ pattaṃ, no’’ ti upadhārayamānā tassa arahattapattiṃ ñatvā uttari upadhāriyamānā,‘‘ mama putto arahattaṃ patvā aho vata me ayaṃ upāsikā mahatī patiṭṭhā jātā’’ ti cintetvā,‘‘ atītepi nu kho me ayaṃ patiṭṭhā bhūtapubbā, no’’ ti upadhārento ekūnaattabhāvasataṃ anussari,‘‘ ahaṃ kho pana ekūnaattabhāvasate aññehi saddhiṃ ekato hutvā etaṃ jīvitā voropesiṃ, ayaṃ me ettakaṃ aguṇaṃ disvā‘ aho bhāriyaṃ kammaṃ kataṃ upāsikāyā’’ ti cintesi."
587791,122,878,96,149,1,333,42,"‘‘ Atthi nu kho evaṃ saṃsāre saṃsarantiyā mama puttassa upakāro katapubbo’’ ti upadhārayamānā tato uttariṃ satamaṃ attabhāvaṃ anussaritvā satame attabhāve mayā etassa pādaparicārikāya hutvā etasmiṃ jīvitā voropanaṭṭhāne jīvitadānaṃ dinnaṃ, aho mayā mama puttassa mahāupakāro katapubbo’’ ti gehe nisinnāva uttariṃ visesetvā‘‘ upadhārethā’’ ti āha. "
587792,122,878,150,188,1,282,33,"So dibbāya sotadhātuyā saddaṃ sutvā visesetvā satamaṃ attabhāvaṃ anussaritvā tattha tāya attano jīvitassa dinnabhāvaṃ disvā,‘‘ aho mama imāya mahāupāsikāya upakāro katapubbo’’ ti attamano hutvā tassā tattheva catūsu maggaphalesu pañhaṃ kathetvā anupādisesāya nibbānadhātuyā parinibbāyīti. "
587793,122,879,2,4,1,29,2,Aññatarabhikkhuvatthu dutiyaṃ.
587794,122,880,2,4,1,31,2,3 . Aññataraukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuvatthu 
587795,122,881,2,13,1,106,11,Sududdasan ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā sāvatthiyaṃ viharanto aññataraṃ ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
587796,122,882,2,30,1,167,20,"Satthari kira sāvatthiyaṃ viharante eko seṭṭhiputto attano kulūpagattheraṃ upasaṅkamitvā,‘‘ bhante, ahaṃ dukkhā muccitukāmo, ekaṃ me dukkhato muccanakāraṇaṃ kathethā’’ ti āha."
587797,122,882,31,72,1,234,29,"‘‘ Sādhāvuso, sacesi dukkhā muccitukāmo, salākabhattaṃ dehi, pakkhikabhattaṃ dehi, vassāvāsikaṃ dehi, cīvarādayo paccaye dehi, attano sāpateyyaṃ tayo koṭṭhāse katvā ekena kammantaṃ payojehi, ekena puttadāraṃ posehi, ekaṃ buddhasāsane dehī’’ ti āha. "
587798,122,882,73,89,1,66,10,"So‘‘ sādhu, bhante’’ ti vuttapaṭipāṭiyā sabbaṃ katvā puna theraṃ pucchi–"
587799,122,882,90,102,1,39,7,"‘‘ tato uttariṃ aññaṃ kiṃ karomi, bhante’’ ti?"
587800,122,882,103,117,1,49,8,"‘‘ Āvuso, tīṇi saraṇāni gaṇha, pañca sīlāni gaṇhāhī’’ ti. "
587801,122,882,118,123,1,39,5,Tānipi paṭiggahetvā tato uttariṃ pucchi.
587802,122,882,124,134,1,30,6,‘‘ Tena hi dasa sīlāni gaṇhāhī’’ ti.
587803,122,882,135,144,1,21,4,"‘‘ Sādhu, bhante’’ ti gaṇhi. "
587804,122,882,145,153,1,70,8,So evaṃ anupubbena puññakammassa katattā anupubbaseṭṭhiputto nāma jāto. 
587805,122,882,154,180,1,102,15,"Tato‘‘ uttarimpi kattabbaṃ atthi, bhante’’ ti puna pucchitvā,‘‘ tena hi pabbajāhī’’ ti vutto nikkhamitvā pabbaji. "
587806,122,882,181,185,1,41,4,Tasseko ābhidhammikabhikkhu ācariyo ahosi. 
587807,122,882,186,189,1,25,3,Eko vinayadharo upajjhāyo. 
587808,122,882,190,199,1,84,9,Tassa laddhūpasampadassa ācariyo attano santikaṃ āgatakāle abhidhamme pañhaṃ kathesi–
587809,122,882,200,214,1,55,9,"‘‘ buddhasāsane nāma idaṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭati, idaṃ na vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
587810,122,882,215,222,1,62,7,Upajjhāyopissa attano santikaṃ āgatakāle vinaye pañhaṃ kathesi–
587811,122,882,223,244,1,84,14,"‘‘ buddhasāsane nāma idaṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭati, idaṃ na vaṭṭati, idaṃ kappati, idaṃ na kappatī’’ ti. "
587812,122,882,245,247,1,10,2,So cintesi–
587813,122,882,248,281,1,176,24,"‘‘ aho bhāriyaṃ idaṃ kammaṃ, ahaṃ dukkhā muccitukāmo pabbajito, idha ca mama hatthapasāraṇaṭṭhānampi na paññāyati, gehe ṭhatvāva dukkhā muccituṃ sakkā, mayā gihinā bhavituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
587814,122,882,282,302,1,162,18,"So tato paṭṭhāya ukkaṇṭhito anabhirato dvattiṃsākāre sajjhāyaṃ na karoti, uddesaṃ na gaṇhāti, kiso lūkho dhamanisanthatagatto ālassiyābhibhūto kacchuparikiṇṇo ahosi. "
587815,122,883,2,32,1,197,22,"Atha naṃ daharasāmaṇerā,‘‘ āvuso, kiṃ tvaṃ ṭhitaṭṭhāne ṭhitova nisinnaṭṭhāne nisinnova ahosi, paṇḍurogābhibhūto kiso lūkho dhamanisanthatagatto ālassiyābhibhūto kacchuparikiṇṇo, kiṃ te katan’’ ti pucchiṃsu."
587816,122,883,33,41,1,22,3,"‘‘ Ukkaṇṭhitomhi, āvuso’’ ti."
587817,122,883,42,49,1,13,3,‘‘ Kiṃ kāraṇā’’ ti? 
587818,122,883,50,54,1,23,4,So taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesi. 
587819,122,883,55,59,1,38,4,Te tassa ācariyupajjhāyānaṃ ācikkhiṃsu. 
587820,122,883,60,66,1,50,6,Ācariyupajjhāyā taṃ ādāya satthu santikaṃ agamaṃsu. 
587821,122,883,67,79,1,37,6,"Satthā‘‘ kiṃ, bhikkhave, āgatatthā’’ ti āha."
587822,122,883,80,92,1,49,7,"‘‘ Bhante, ayaṃ bhikkhu tumhākaṃ sāsane ukkaṇṭhito’’ ti."
587823,122,883,93,101,1,20,4,‘‘ Evaṃ kira bhikkhū’’ ti.
587824,122,883,102,110,1,13,3,"‘‘ Āma, bhante’’ ti."
587825,122,883,111,118,1,13,3,‘‘ Kiṃ kāraṇā’’ ti?
587826,122,883,119,162,1,244,29,"‘‘ Ahaṃ, bhante, dukkhā muccitukāmova pabbajito, tassa me ācariyo abhidhammakathaṃ kathesi, upajjhāyo vinayakathaṃ kathesi, svāhaṃ‘ idha me hatthapasāraṇaṭṭhānampi natthi, gihinā hutvā sakkā dukkhā muccituṃ, gihi bhavissāmī’ ti sanniṭṭhānamakāsiṃ, bhante’’ ti."
587827,122,883,163,180,1,83,10,"‘‘ Sace tvaṃ, bhikkhu, ekameva rakkhituṃ sakkhissasi, avasesānaṃ rakkhanakiccaṃ natthī’’ ti."
587828,122,883,181,189,1,13,3,"‘‘ Kiṃ, bhante’’ ti?"
587829,122,883,190,199,1,39,5,‘‘ Tava cittameva rakkhituṃ sakkhissasī’’ ti.
587830,122,883,200,208,1,21,3,"‘‘ Sakkhissāmi, bhante’’ ti."
587831,122,883,209,228,1,91,14,"‘‘ Tena hi attano cittameva rakkhāhi, sakkā dukkhā muccitun’’ ti imaṃ ovādaṃ datvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
587832,122,884,2,4,1,0,0,36.
587833,122,885,2,9,1,40,4,"‘ ‘ Sududdasaṃ sunipuṇaṃ, yatthakāmanipātinaṃ; "
587834,122,886,2,12,1,52,7,"Cittaṃ rakkhetha medhāvī, cittaṃ guttaṃ sukhāvahan’’ ti. "
587835,122,887,2,9,1,36,5,Tattha sududdasan ti suṭṭhu duddasaṃ. 
587836,122,887,10,15,1,40,5,Sunipuṇan ti suṭṭhu nipuṇaṃ paramasaṇhaṃ. 
587837,122,887,16,24,1,112,8,Yatthakāmanipātinan ti jātiādīni anoloketvā labhitabbālabhitabbayuttāyuttaṭṭhānesu yattha katthaci nipatanasīlaṃ. 
587838,122,887,25,42,1,131,15,"Cittaṃ rakkhetha {medhāvī}ti andhabālo dummedho attano cittaṃ rakkhituṃ samattho nāma natthi, cittavasiko hutvā anayabyasanaṃ pāpuṇāti. "
587839,122,887,43,54,1,77,10,"Medhāvī pana paṇḍitova cittaṃ rakkhituṃ sakkoti, tasmā tvampi cittameva gopehi. "
587840,122,887,55,61,1,66,6,Idañhi cittaṃ guttaṃ sukhāvahaṃ maggaphalanibbānasukhāni āvahatīti. 
587841,122,888,2,17,1,119,13,"Desanāpariyosāne so bhikkhu sotāpattiphalaṃ pāpuṇi, aññepi bahū sotāpannādayo ahesuṃ, desanā mahājanassa sātthikā ahosīti. "
587842,122,889,2,4,1,39,2,Aññataraukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuvatthu tatiyaṃ.
587843,122,890,2,4,1,36,2,4 . Saṅgharakkhitabhāgineyyattheravatthu 
587844,122,891,2,14,1,107,12,Dūraṅgaman ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā sāvatthiyaṃ viharanto saṅgharakkhitaṃ nāma bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
587845,122,892,2,17,1,155,15,Sāvatthiyaṃ kireko kulaputto satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā nikkhamitvā pabbajito laddhūpasampado saṅgharakkhitatthero nāma hutvā katipāheneva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
587846,122,892,18,26,1,58,7,Tassa kaniṭṭhabhaginī puttaṃ labhitvā therassa nāmaṃ akāsi. 
587847,122,892,27,101,1,537,56,"So bhāgineyyasaṅgharakkhito nāma hutvā vayappatto therasseva santike pabbajitvā laddhūpasampado aññatarasmiṃ gāmakārāme vassaṃ upagantvā,‘‘ ekaṃ sattahatthaṃ, ekaṃ aṭṭhahatthan’’ ti dve vassāvāsikasāṭake labhitvā aṭṭhahatthaṃ‘‘ upajjhāyassa me bhavissatī’’ ti sallakkhetvā‘‘ sattahatthaṃ mayhaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti cintetvā vuṭṭhavasso‘‘ upajjhāyaṃ passissāmī’’ ti āgacchanto antarāmagge piṇḍāya caranto āgantvā there vihāraṃ anāgateyeva vihāraṃ pavisitvā therassa divāṭṭhānaṃ sammajjitvā pādodakaṃ upaṭṭhapetvā āsanaṃ paññapetvā āgamanamaggaṃ olokento nisīdi. "
587848,122,892,102,146,1,254,30,"Athassāgamanabhāvaṃ disvā paccuggamanaṃ katvā pattacīvaraṃ paṭiggahetvā,‘‘ nisīdatha, bhante’’ ti theraṃ nisīdāpetvā tālavaṇṭaṃ ādāya bījitvā pānīyaṃ datvā pāde dhovitvā taṃ sāṭakaṃ ānetvā pādamūle ṭhapetvā,‘‘ bhante, imaṃ paribhuñjathā’’ ti vatvā bījayamāno aṭṭhāsi. "
587849,122,893,2,6,1,18,4,Atha naṃ thero āha–
587850,122,893,7,20,1,62,7,"‘‘ saṅgharakkhita, mayhaṃ cīvaraṃ paripuṇṇaṃ, tvameva paribhuñjā’’ ti."
587851,122,893,21,37,1,84,10,"‘‘ Bhante, mayā laddhakālato paṭṭhāya ayaṃ tumhākameva sallakkhito, paribhogaṃ karothā’’ ti."
587852,122,893,38,53,1,63,8,"‘‘ Hotu, saṅgharakkhita, paripuṇṇaṃ me cīvaraṃ, tvameva paribhuñjā’’ ti."
587853,122,893,54,70,1,74,10,"‘‘ Bhante, mā evaṃ karotha, tumhehi paribhutte mayhaṃ mahapphalaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti. "
587854,122,893,71,80,1,58,8,Atha naṃ tassa punappunaṃ kathentassapi thero na icchiyeva. 
587855,122,894,2,7,1,34,5,Evaṃ so bījayamāno ṭhitova cintesi–
587856,122,894,8,25,1,116,13,"‘‘ ahaṃ therassa gihikāle bhāgineyyo, pabbajitakāle saddhivihāriko, evampi mayā saddhiṃ upajjhāyo paribhogaṃ na kattukāmo. "
587857,122,894,26,40,1,80,11,"Imasmiṃ mayā saddhiṃ paribhogaṃ akaronte kiṃ me samaṇabhāvena, gihi bhavissāmī’’ ti. "
587858,122,894,41,43,1,17,2,Athassa etadahosi–
587859,122,894,44,58,1,63,9,"‘‘ dussaṇṭhāpito gharāvāso, kiṃ nu kho katvā gihibhūto jīvissāmī’’ ti. "
587860,122,894,59,61,1,12,2,Tato cintesi–
