587862,122,894,94,115,1,167,20,"Athassa mama mātulassa nāmaṃ katvā cūḷayānake nisīdāpetvā mama puttañca bhariyañca ādāya mātulaṃ vandituṃ āgamissāmi, āgacchante antarāmagge mama bhariyaṃ evaṃ vakkhāmi–"
587863,122,894,116,124,1,36,6,‘ ānehi tāva me puttaṃ vahissāminan’ ti. 
587864,122,894,125,153,1,136,21,"Sā‘ kiṃ te puttena, ehi, imaṃ yānakaṃ pājehī’ ti vatvā puttaṃ gahetvā,‘ ahaṃ nessāmi nan’ ti netvā sandhāretuṃ asakkontī cakkapathe chaḍḍessati. "
