587892,122,904,2,13,1,104,9,{Anavaṭṭhitacittassā}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā sāvatthiyaṃ viharanto cittahatthattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
587893,122,905,2,36,1,260,29,"Eko kira sāvatthivāsī kulaputto naṭṭhagoṇaṃ pariyesanto araññaṃ pavisitvā majjhanhike kāle goṇaṃ disvā goyūthe vissajjetvā,‘‘ avassaṃ ayyānaṃ santike āhāramattaṃ labhissāmī’’ ti khuppipāsāpīḷito vihāraṃ pavisitvā bhikkhūnaṃ santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
587894,122,905,37,62,1,146,19,"Tasmiṃ kho pana samaye bhikkhūnaṃ avakkārapātiyaṃ bhuttāvasesakaṃ bhattaṃ hoti, te taṃ chātakapīḷitaṃ disvā,‘‘ ito bhattaṃ gahetvā bhuñjāhī’’ ti vadiṃsu. "
587895,122,905,63,99,1,200,25,"Buddhakāle ca pana anekasūpabyañjanaṃ bhattaṃ uppajjati, so tato yāpanamattaṃ gahetvā bhuñjitvā pānīyaṃ pivitvā hatthe dhovitvā bhikkhū vanditvā,‘‘ kiṃ, bhante, ajja, ayyā, nimantanaṭṭhānaṃ agamaṃsū’’ ti pucchi."
587896,122,905,100,114,1,61,8,"‘‘ Natthi, upāsaka, bhikkhū imināva nīhārena nibaddhaṃ labhantī’’ ti. "
587897,122,905,115,150,1,223,28,"So‘‘ mayaṃ uṭṭhāya samuṭṭhāya rattindivaṃ nibaddhaṃ kammaṃ karontāpi evaṃ madhurabyañjanaṃ bhattaṃ na labhāma, ime kira nibaddhaṃ bhuñjanti, kiṃ me gihibhāvena, bhikkhu bhavissāmī’’ ti cintetvā bhikkhū upasaṅkamitvā pabbajjaṃ yāci. "
587898,122,905,151,162,1,44,7,Atha naṃ bhikkhū‘‘ sādhu upāsakā’’ ti pabbājesuṃ. 
