587960,122,919,72,87,1,135,15,Imināva nīhārena nāḷimattaṃ varakacorakañca kuṇṭhakudālañca nissāya sattavāre gihī hutvā sattavāre pabbajitvā sattame pana vāre cintesi–
587961,122,919,88,106,1,93,13,"‘‘ ahaṃ cha vāre imaṃ kuṇṭhakudālaṃ nissāya gihī hutvā pabbajito, katthacideva naṃ chaḍḍessāmī’’ ti. "
587962,122,919,107,168,1,405,48,"So gaṅgāya tīraṃ gantvā,‘‘ patitaṭṭhānaṃ passanto otaritvā gaṇheyyaṃ, yathāssa patitaṭṭhānaṃ na passāmi, tathā naṃ chaḍḍessāmī’’ ti cintetvā nāḷimattaṃ bījaṃ pilotikāya bandhitvā pilotikaṃ kudālaphalake bandhitvā kudālaṃ aggadaṇḍake gahetvā gaṅgāya tīre ṭhito akkhīni nimīletvā uparisīse tikkhattuṃ āvijjhitvā gaṅgāyaṃ khipitvā nivattitvā olokento patitaṭṭhānaṃ adisvā‘‘ jitaṃ me, jitaṃ me’’ ti tikkhattuṃ saddamakāsi. "
587963,122,920,2,17,1,130,15,Tasmiṃ khaṇe bārāṇasirājā paccantaṃ vūpasametvā āgantvā nadītīre khandhāvāraṃ nivāsetvā nhānatthāya nadiṃ otiṇṇo taṃ saddaṃ assosi. 
587964,122,920,18,67,1,182,32,"Rājūnañca nāma‘‘ jitaṃ me’’ ti saddo amanāpo hoti, so tassa santikaṃ gantvā,‘‘ ahaṃ idāni amittamaddanaṃ katvā‘ jitaṃ me’ ti āgato, tvaṃ pana‘ jitaṃ me, jitaṃ me’ ti viravasi, kiṃ nāmetan’’ ti pucchi. "
587965,122,920,68,102,1,173,26,"Kudālapaṇḍito‘‘ tvaṃ bāhirakacore jini, tayā jitaṃ puna avajitameva hoti, mayā pana ajjhattiko lobhacoro jito, so puna maṃ na jinissati, tasseva jayo sādhū’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha–"
587966,122,921,2,13,1,44,9,"‘ ‘ Na taṃ jitaṃ sādhu jitaṃ, yaṃ jitaṃ avajīyati; "
587967,122,922,2,24,1,49,9,"Taṃ kho jitaṃ sādhu jitaṃ, yaṃ jitaṃ nāvajīyatī’’ ti.( jā.1.1.70); "
587968,122,923,2,13,1,95,11,Taṃ khaṇaṃyeva ca gaṅgaṃ olokento āpokasiṇaṃ nibbattetvā adhigataviseso ākāse pallaṅkena nisīdi. 
587969,122,923,14,25,1,91,10,Rājā mahāpurisassa dhammakathaṃ sutvā vanditvā pabbajjaṃ yācitvā saddhiṃ balakāyena pabbaji. 
587970,122,923,26,29,1,24,3,Yojanamattā parisā ahosi. 
587971,122,923,30,79,1,304,37,"Aparopi sāmantarājā tassa pabbajitabhāvaṃ sutvā,‘‘ tassa rajjaṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti āgantvā tathā samiddhaṃ nagaraṃ suññaṃ disvā,‘‘ evarūpaṃ nagaraṃ chaḍḍetvā pabbajito rājā orake ṭhāne na pabbajissati, mayāpi pabbajituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti cintetvā tattha gantvā mahāpurisaṃ upasaṅkamitvā pabbajjaṃ yācitvā saparivāro pabbaji. "
587972,122,923,80,85,1,40,5,Eteneva nīhārena satta rājāno pabbajiṃsu. 
587973,122,923,86,89,1,26,3,Sattayojaniko assamo ahosi. 
587974,122,923,90,99,1,61,8,Satta rājāno bhoge chaḍḍetvā ettakaṃ janaṃ gahetvā pabbajiṃsu. 
587975,122,923,100,105,1,57,5,Mahāpuriso brahmacariyavāsaṃ vasitvā brahmalokūpago ahosi. 
587976,122,924,2,25,1,109,15,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā,‘‘ ahaṃ, bhikkhave, tadā kudālapaṇḍito ahosiṃ, kilesā nāmete evaṃ bhāriyā’’ ti āha. "
