587978,122,926,2,4,1,22,2,6 . Pañcasatabhikkhuvatthu 
587979,122,927,2,13,1,103,11,Kumbhūpaman ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā sāvatthiyaṃ viharanto āraddhavipassake bhikkhū ārabbha kathesi. 
587980,122,928,2,25,1,163,18,"Sāvatthiyaṃ kira pañcasatā bhikkhū satthu santike yāva arahattā kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā,‘‘ samaṇadhammaṃ karissāmā’’ ti yojanasatamaggaṃ gantvā ekaṃ mahāvāsagāmaṃ agamaṃsu. "
587981,122,928,26,98,1,367,46,"Atha te manussā disvā paññattāsane nisīdāpetvā paṇītehi yāgubhattādīhi parivisitvā,‘‘ kahaṃ, bhante, gacchathā’’ ti pucchitvā,‘‘ yathāphāsukaṭṭhānan’’ ti vutte,‘‘ bhante, imaṃ temāsaṃ idheva vasatha, mayampi tumhākaṃ santike saraṇesu patiṭṭhāya pañca sīlāni rakkhissāmā’’ ti yācitvā tesaṃ adhivāsanaṃ viditvā,‘‘ avidūre ṭhāne mahanto vanasaṇḍo atthi, ettha vasatha, bhante’’ ti vatvā uyyojesuṃ. "
587982,122,928,99,103,1,32,4,Bhikkhū taṃ vanasaṇḍaṃ pavisiṃsu. 
587983,122,928,104,154,1,280,36,"Tasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe adhivatthā devatā‘‘ sīlavanto, ayyā, imaṃ vanasaṇḍaṃ anuppattā, ayuttaṃ kho pana asmākaṃ ayyesu idha vasantesu puttadāre gahetvā rukkhe abhiruyha vasitun’’ ti rukkhato otaritvā bhūmiyaṃ nisīditvā cintayiṃsu,‘‘ ayyā, imasmiṃ ṭhāne ajjekarattiṃ vasitvā addhā sve gamissantī’’ ti. "
587984,122,928,155,164,1,77,9,Bhikkhūpi punadivase antogāme piṇḍāya caritvā puna tameva vanasaṇḍaṃ āgamiṃsu. 
587985,122,928,165,195,1,178,21,"Devatā‘‘ bhikkhusaṅgho svātanāya kenaci nimantito bhavissati, tasmā punāgacchati , ajja gamanaṃ na bhavissati, sve gamissati maññe’’ ti iminā upāyena aḍḍhamāsamattaṃ bhūmiyameva acchiṃsu. "
587986,122,929,2,4,1,15,2,Tato cintayiṃsu–
587987,122,929,5,42,1,234,30,"‘‘ bhadantā imaṃ temāsaṃ idheva maññe vasissanti, idheva kho pana imesu vasantesu amhākaṃ rukkhe abhiruhitvā nisīditumpi na yuttaṃ, temāsaṃ puttadāre gahetvā bhūmiyaṃ nisīdanaṭṭhānānipi dukkhāni, kiñci katvā ime bhikkhū palāpetuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
587988,122,929,43,56,1,129,13,Tā tesu tesu rattiṭṭhānadivāṭṭhānesu ceva caṅkamanakoṭīsu ca chinnasīsāni kabandhāni dassetuṃ amanussasaddañca bhāvetuṃ ārabhiṃsu. 
587989,122,929,57,61,1,42,4,Bhikkhūnaṃ khipitakāsādayo rogā pavattiṃsu. 
587990,122,929,62,132,1,385,46,"Te aññamaññaṃ‘‘ tuyhaṃ, āvuso, kiṃ rujjatī’’ ti pucchantā,‘‘ mayhaṃ khipitarogo, mayhaṃ kāso’’ ti vatvā,‘‘ āvuso, ahaṃ ajja caṅkamanakoṭiyaṃ chinnasīsaṃ addasaṃ, ahaṃ rattiṭṭhāne kabandhaṃ addasaṃ , ahaṃ divāṭṭhāne amanussasaddaṃ assosiṃ, parivajjetabbayuttakamidaṃ ṭhānaṃ, amhākaṃ idha aphāsukaṃ ahosi, satthu santikaṃ gamissāmā’’ ti nikkhamitvā anupubbena satthu santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. "
587991,122,930,2,6,1,18,4,Atha ne satthā āha–
587992,122,930,7,21,1,53,8,"‘‘ kiṃ, bhikkhave, tasmiṃ ṭhāne vasituṃ na sakkhissathā’’ ti?"
587993,122,930,22,55,1,191,23,"‘‘ Āma, bhante, amhākaṃ tasmiṃ ṭhāne vasantānaṃ evarūpāni bheravārammaṇāni upaṭṭhahanti, evarūpaṃ aphāsukaṃ hoti, tena mayaṃ‘ vajjetabbayuttakamidaṃ ṭhānan’ ti taṃ chaḍḍetvā tumhākaṃ santikaṃ āgatā’’ ti."
587994,122,930,56,67,1,45,6,"‘‘ Bhikkhave, tattheva tumhākaṃ gantuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti."
587995,122,930,68,77,1,18,4,"‘‘ Na sakkā, bhante’’ ti."
587996,122,930,78,94,1,73,10,"‘‘ Bhikkhave, tumhe āvudhaṃ aggahetvā gatā, idāni āvudhaṃ gahetvā gacchathā’’ ti."
587997,122,930,95,103,1,22,3,"‘‘ Katarāvudhaṃ, bhante’’ ti? "
587998,122,930,104,121,1,77,12,"Satthā‘‘ ahaṃ āvudhaṃ vo dassāmi, mayā dinnaṃ āvudhaṃ gahetvā gacchathā’’ ti vatvā–"
587999,122,931,2,10,1,53,6,"‘ ‘ Karaṇīyamatthakusalena, yanta santaṃ padaṃ abhisamecca; "
588000,122,932,2,31,1,53,10,"Sakko ujū ca suhujū ca, suvaco cassa mudu anatimānī’’ ti.( khu. pā.9.1; su. ni.143)– "
588001,122,933,2,23,1,134,15,"Sakalaṃ mettasuttaṃ kathetvā,‘‘ bhikkhave, imaṃ tumhe bahi vihārassa vanasaṇḍato paṭṭhāya sajjhāyantā antovihāraṃ paviseyyāthā’’ ti uyyojesi. "
588002,122,933,24,38,1,126,14,Te satthāraṃ vanditvā nikkhamitvā anupubbena taṃ ṭhānaṃ patvā bahivihāre gaṇasajjhāyaṃ katvā sajjhāyamānā vanasaṇḍaṃ pavisiṃsu. 
588003,122,933,39,65,1,223,20,"Sakalavanasaṇḍe devatā mettacittaṃ paṭilabhitvā tesaṃ paccuggamanaṃ katvā pattacīvarapaṭiggahaṇaṃ āpucchiṃsu, hatthapādasambāhanaṃ āpucchiṃsu, tesaṃ tattha tattha ārakkhaṃ saṃvidahiṃsu, pakkadhūpanatelaṃ viya sannisinnā ahesuṃ. "
588004,122,933,66,70,1,34,4,Katthaci amanussasaddo nāma nāhosi. 
588005,122,933,71,76,1,37,5,Tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ cittaṃ ekaggaṃ ahosi. 
588006,122,933,77,100,1,190,18,"Te rattiṭṭhānadivāṭṭhānesu nisinnā vipassanāya cittaṃ otāretvā attani khayavayaṃ paṭṭhapetvā,‘‘ ayaṃ attabhāvo nāma bhijjanakaṭṭhena athāvaraṭṭhena kulālabhājanasadiso’’ ti vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhayiṃsu. "
588007,122,933,101,142,1,321,34,"Sammāsambuddho gandhakuṭiyā nisinnova tesaṃ vipassanāya āraddhabhāvaṃ ñatvā te bhikkhū āmantetvā,‘‘ evameva, bhikkhave, ayaṃ attabhāvo nāma bhijjanakaṭṭhena athāvaraṭṭhena kulālabhājanasadiso evā’’ ti vatvā obhāsaṃ pharitvā yojanasate ṭhitopi abhimukhe nisinno viya chabbaṇṇaraṃsiyo vissajjetvā dissamānena rūpena imaṃ gāthamāha– "
588008,122,934,2,4,1,0,0,40.
588009,122,935,2,11,1,61,7,"‘ ‘ Kumbhūpamaṃ kāyamiṃma viditvā, nagarūpamaṃ cittamidaṃ ṭhapetvā; "
588010,122,936,2,13,1,60,8,"Yodhetha māraṃ paññāvudhena, jitañca rakkhe anivesano siyā’’ ti. "
588011,122,937,2,14,1,142,11,Tattha kumbhūpaman ti abaladubbalaṭṭhena anaddhaniyatāvakālikaṭṭhena imaṃ kesādisamūhasaṅkhātaṃ kāyaṃ kumbhūpamaṃ kulālabhājanasadisaṃ viditvā. 
588012,122,937,15,79,1,571,54,"Nagarūpamaṃ cittamidaṃ {ṭhapetvā}ti nagaraṃ nāma bahiddhā thiraṃ hoti, gambhīraparikhaṃ pākāraparikkhittaṃ dvāraṭṭālakayuttaṃ, antosuvibhattavīthicatukkasiṅghāṭakasampannaṃ antarāpaṇaṃ, taṃ‘‘ vilumpissāmā’’ ti bahiddhā corā āgantvā pavisituṃ asakkontā pabbataṃ āsajja paṭihatā viya gacchanti, evameva paṇḍito kulaputto attano vipassanācittaṃ thiraṃ nagarasadisaṃ katvā ṭhapetvā nagare ṭhito ekatodhārādinānappakārāvudhena coragaṇaṃ viya vipassanāmayena ca ariyamaggamayena ca paññāvudhena taṃtaṃmaggavajjhaṃ kilesamāraṃ paṭibāhanto taṃ taṃ kilesamāraṃ yodhetha, pahareyyāthāti attho. "
588013,122,937,80,97,1,229,16,Jitañca {rakkhe}ti jitañca uppāditaṃ taruṇavipassanaṃ āvāsasappāyautusappāyabhojanasappāyapuggalasappāyadhammassavanasappāyādīni āsevanto antarantarā samāpattiṃ samāpajjitvā tato vuṭṭhāya suddhacittena saṅkhāre sammasanto rakkheyya. 
588014,122,938,2,8,1,33,4,Anivesano {siyā}ti anālayo bhaveyya. 
588015,122,938,9,49,1,292,37,"Yathā nāma yodho saṅgāmasīse balakoṭṭhakaṃ katvā amittehi saddhiṃ yujjhanto chāto vā pipāsito vā hutvā sannāhe vā sithile āvudhe vā patite balakoṭṭhakaṃ pavisitvā vissamitvā bhuñjitvā pivitvā sannahitvā āvudhaṃ gahetvā puna nikkhamitvā yujjhanto parasenaṃ maddati, ajitaṃ jināti, jitaṃ rakkhati. "
588016,122,938,50,86,1,292,30,"So hi sace balakoṭṭhake ṭhito evaṃ vissamanto taṃ assādento accheyya, rajjaṃ parahatthagataṃ kareyya, evameva, bhikkhu, paṭiladdhaṃ taruṇavipassanaṃ punappunaṃ samāpattiṃ samāpajjitvā tato vuṭṭhāya suddhacittena saṅkhāre sammasanto rakkhituṃ sakkoti, uttarimaggaphalapaṭilābhena kilesamāraṃ jināti. "
588017,122,938,87,103,1,120,14,"Sace pana so samāpattimeva assādeti, suddhacittena punappunaṃ saṅkhāre na sammasati, maggaphalapaṭivedhaṃ kātuṃ na sakkoti. "
588018,122,938,104,121,1,123,15,"Tasmā rakkhitabbayuttakaṃ rakkhanto anivesano siyā, samāpattiṃ nivesanaṃ katvā tattha na niveseyya, ālayaṃ na kareyyāti attho."
588019,122,938,122,137,1,73,11,‘‘ Addhā tumhepi evaṃ karothā’’ ti evaṃ satthā tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammaṃ desesi. 
588020,122,939,2,18,1,171,16,Desanāvasāne pañcasatā bhikkhū nisinnaṭṭhāne nisinnāyeva saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ patvā tathāgatassa suvaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ sarīraṃ vaṇṇayantā thomentā vandantāva āgacchiṃsūti. 
588021,122,940,2,4,1,31,2,Pañcasatabhikkhuvatthu chaṭṭhaṃ.
588022,122,941,2,4,1,26,2,7 . Pūtigattatissattheravatthu 
588023,122,942,2,15,1,107,11,Aciraṃ vatayaṃ {kāyo}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā sāvatthiyaṃ viharanto pūtigattatissattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
588024,122,943,2,20,1,130,17,"Eko kira sāvatthivāsī kulaputto satthu santike dhammaṃ sutvā sāsane uraṃ datvā pabbajito, so laddhūpasampado tissatthero nāma ahosi. "
588025,122,943,21,28,1,50,7,Gacchante gacchante kāle tassa sarīre rogo udapādi. 
588026,122,943,29,32,1,31,3,Sāsapamattiyo piḷakā uṭṭhahiṃsu. 
588027,122,943,33,47,1,147,13,"Tā anupubbena muggamattā kalāyamattā kolaṭṭhimattā āmalakamattā beḷuvasalāṭumattā beḷuvamattā hutvā pabhijjiṃsu, sakalasarīraṃ chiddāvachiddaṃ ahosi. "
588028,122,943,48,52,1,43,4,Pūtigattatissatthero tvevassa nāmaṃ udapādi. 
588029,122,943,53,57,1,36,4,Athassa aparabhāge aṭṭhīni bhijjiṃsu. 
588030,122,943,58,62,1,22,3,So appaṭijaggiyo ahosi. 
588031,122,943,63,67,1,60,4,Nivāsanapārupanaṃ pubbalohitamakkhitaṃ jālapūvasadisaṃ ahosi. 
588032,122,943,68,72,1,53,4,Saddhivihārikādayo paṭijaggituṃ asakkontā chaḍḍayiṃsu. 
588033,122,943,73,77,1,23,4,So anātho hutvā nipajji. 
588034,122,944,2,9,1,55,7,Buddhānañca nāma dve vāre lokavolokanaṃ avijahitaṃ hoti. 
588035,122,944,10,28,1,174,17,"Paccūsakāle lokaṃ volokentā cakkavāḷamukhavaṭṭito paṭṭhāya gandhakuṭiabhimukhaṃ ñāṇaṃ katvā olokenti, sāyaṃ olokentā gandhakuṭito paṭṭhāya bāhirābhimukhaṃ ñāṇaṃ katvā olokenti. "
588036,122,944,29,37,1,74,8,Tasmiṃ pana samaye bhagavato ñāṇajālassa anto pūtigattatissatthero paññāyi. 
588037,122,944,38,79,1,310,34,"Satthā tassa bhikkhuno arahattassa upanissayaṃ disvā,‘‘ ayaṃ saddhivihārikādīhi chaḍḍito, idānissa maṃ ṭhapetvā aññaṃ paṭisaraṇaṃ natthī’’ ti gandhakuṭito nikkhamitvā vihāracārikaṃ caramāno viya aggisālaṃ gantvā ukkhaliṃ dhovitvā udakaṃ datvā uddhanaṃ āropetvā udakassa tattabhāvaṃ āgamayamāno aggisālāyameva aṭṭhāsi. "
588038,122,944,80,106,1,151,18,"Tattabhāvaṃ jānitvā gantvā tassa bhikkhuno nipannamañcakoṭiyaṃ gaṇhi, tadā bhikkhū‘‘ apetha, bhante, mayaṃ gaṇhissāmā’’ ti mañcakaṃ gahetvā aggisālaṃ ānayiṃsu. "
588039,122,944,107,121,1,129,14,Satthā ambaṇaṃ āharāpetvā uṇhodakaṃ āsiñcitvā tehi bhikkhūhi tassa pārupanaṃ gāhāpetvā uṇhodake maddāpetvā mandātape vissajjāpesi. 
588040,122,944,122,135,1,107,12,"Athassa santike ṭhatvā sarīraṃ uṇhodakena temetvā ghaṃsitvā nhāpesi, tassa nahānapariyosāne pārupanaṃ sukkhi. "
588041,122,944,136,145,1,76,9,Atha naṃ taṃ nivāsāpetvā nivatthakāsāvaṃ udake maddāpetvā ātape vissajjāpesi. 
588042,122,944,146,152,1,44,6,Athassa gatte udake chinnamatte tampi sukkhi. 
588043,122,944,153,163,1,84,10,So ekaṃ kāsāvaṃ nivāsetvā ekaṃ pārupitvā sallahukasarīro ekaggacitto mañcake nipajji. 
588044,122,944,164,188,1,140,19,"Satthā tassa ussīsake ṭhatvā,‘‘ bhikkhu ayaṃ tava kāyo apetaviññāṇo nirupakāro hutvā kaliṅgaraṃ viya pathaviyaṃ sessatī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
588045,122,945,2,4,1,0,0,41.
588046,122,946,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Aciraṃ vatayaṃ kāyo, pathaviṃ adhisessati; "
588047,122,947,2,10,1,46,5,"Chuddho apetaviññāṇo, niratthaṃva kaliṅgaran’’ ti. "
588048,122,948,2,21,1,129,16,"Tattha aciraṃ {vatā}ti bhikkhu na cirasseva ayaṃ kāyo pathaviṃ adhisessati, imissā pakatisayanena sayitāya pathaviyā upari sayissati . "
588049,122,948,22,32,1,69,7,"{Chuddho}ti apaviddho, apagataviññāṇatāya tuccho hutvā sessatīti dasseti. "
588050,122,948,33,35,1,9,2,Yathā kiṃ? 
588051,122,948,36,42,1,65,6,Niratthaṃva kaliṅgaraṃ nirupakāraṃ niratthakaṃ kaṭṭhakhaṇḍaṃ viya. 
588052,122,948,43,65,1,216,21,"Dabbasambhāratthikā hi manussā araññaṃ pavisitvā ujukaṃ ujukasaṇṭhānena vaṅkaṃ vaṅkasaṇṭhānena chinditvā dabbasambhāraṃ gaṇhanti, avasesaṃ pana susirañca pūtikañca asārakañca gaṇṭhijātañca chinditvā tattheva chaḍḍenti. "
588053,122,948,66,82,1,124,14,"Aññe dabbasambhāratthikā āgantvā taṃ gahetāro nāma natthi, oloketvā attano upakārakameva gaṇhanti, itaraṃ pathavīgatameva hoti. "
588054,122,948,83,97,1,104,14,Taṃ pana tena tena upāyena mañcapaṭipādakaṃ vā pādakathalikaṃ vā phalakapīṭhaṃ vā kātuṃ sakkāpi bhaveyya. 
588055,122,948,98,121,1,220,22,"Imasmiṃ pana attabhāve dvattiṃsāya koṭṭhāsesu ekakoṭṭhāsopi mañcapaṭipādakādivasena aññena vā upakāramukhena gayhūpago nāma natthi, kevalaṃ niratthaṃva kaliṅgaraṃ ayaṃ kāyo apagataviññāṇo katipāheneva pathaviyaṃ sessatīti. "
588056,122,949,2,14,1,103,10,"Desanāvasāne pūtigattatissatthero saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ pāpuṇi, aññepi bahū sotāpannādayo ahesuṃ. "
588057,122,949,15,19,1,37,4,Theropi arahattaṃ patvāva parinibbāyi. 
588058,122,949,20,28,1,68,8,Satthā tassa sarīrakiccaṃ kārāpetvā dhātuyo gahetvā cetiyaṃ kārāpesi. 
588059,122,949,29,32,1,27,3,Bhikkhū satthāraṃ pucchiṃsu–
588060,122,949,33,43,1,45,5,"‘‘ bhante, pūtigattatissatthero kuhiṃ nibbatto’’ ti."
588061,122,949,44,52,1,24,3,"‘‘ Parinibbuto, bhikkhave’’ ti."
588062,122,949,53,80,1,176,20,"‘‘ Bhante, evarūpassa pana arahattūpanissayasampannassa bhikkhuno kiṃ kāraṇā gattaṃ putikaṃ jātaṃ, kiṃ kāraṇā aṭṭhīni bhinnāni, kimassa kāraṇaṃ arahattassa upanissayabhāvaṃ pattan’’ ti?"
588063,122,949,81,93,1,61,7,"‘‘ Bhikkhave, sabbametaṃ etassa attanā katakammeneva nibbattan’’ ti."
588064,122,949,94,106,1,29,6,"‘‘ Kiṃ pana tena, bhante, katan’’ ti?"
588065,122,949,107,120,1,41,7,"‘‘ Tena hi, bhikkhave, suṇāthā’’ ti atītaṃ āhari– "
588066,122,950,2,12,1,88,9,Ayaṃ kassapasammāsambuddhakāle sākuṇiko hutvā bahū sakuṇe vadhitvā issarajanaṃ upaṭṭhahi. 
588067,122,950,13,46,1,205,26,"Tesaṃ dinnāvasese vikkiṇāti,‘‘ vikkitāvasesā māretvā ṭhapitā pūtikā bhavissantī’’ ti yathā uppatituṃ na sakkonti, tathā tesaṃ jaṅghaṭṭhīni ca pakkhaṭṭhīni ca bhinditvā rāsiṃ katvā ṭhapeti, te punadivase vikkiṇāti. "
588068,122,950,47,53,1,52,6,Atibahūnaṃ pana laddhakāle attanopi atthāya pacāpeti. 
588069,122,950,54,63,1,80,9,Tassekadivasaṃ rasabhojane pakke eko khīṇāsavo piṇḍāya caranto gehadvāre aṭṭhāsi. 
588070,122,950,64,117,1,293,38,"So theraṃ disvā cittaṃ pasādetvā,‘‘ mayā bahū pāṇā māretvā khāditā, ayyo ca me gehadvāre ṭhito, antogehe ca rasabhojanaṃ saṃvijjati, piṇḍapātamassa dassāmī’’ ti tassa pattaṃ ādāya pūretvā rasapiṇḍapātaṃ datvā theraṃ pañcapatiṭṭhitena vanditvā,‘‘ bhante, tumhehi diṭṭhadhammassa matthakaṃ pāpuṇeyyan’’ ti āha. "
588071,122,950,118,128,1,35,6,Thero‘‘ evaṃ hotū’’ ti anumodanaṃ akāsi.
588072,122,950,129,156,1,198,19,"‘‘ Bhikkhave, tadā katakammavasenetaṃ tissassa nipphannaṃ, sakuṇānaṃ aṭṭhibhedananissandena tissassa gattañca pūtikaṃ jātaṃ, aṭṭhīni ca bhinnāni, khīṇāsavassa rasapiṇḍapātadānanissandena arahattaṃ patto’’ ti. "
588073,122,951,2,4,1,35,2,Pūtigattatissattheravatthu sattamaṃ.
588074,122,952,2,4,1,19,2,8 . Nandagopālakavatthu 
588075,122,953,2,12,1,85,10,Diso disan ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā kosalajanapade nandagopālakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
588076,122,954,2,15,1,109,12,Sāvatthiyaṃ kira anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatino nando nāma gopālako goyūthaṃ rakkhati aḍḍho mahaddhano mahābhogo. 
588077,122,954,16,30,1,108,13,"So kira yathā keṇiyo jaṭilo pabbajjāvesena, evaṃ gopālakattena rājabaliṃ pariharanto attano kuṭumbaṃ rakkhati. "
588078,122,954,31,52,1,153,18,"So kālena kālaṃ pañca gorase ādāya anāthapiṇḍikassa santikaṃ āgantvā satthāraṃ passati, dhammaṃ suṇāti, attano vasanaṭṭhānaṃ āgamanatthāya satthāraṃ yācati. "
588079,122,954,53,71,1,190,18,Satthā tassa ñāṇaparipākaṃ āgamayamāno āgantvā paripakkabhāvaṃ ñatvā ekadivasaṃ mahābhikkhusaṅghaparivuto cārikaṃ caranto maggā okkamma tassa vasanaṭṭhānāsanne aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle nisīdi. 
588080,122,954,72,87,1,155,15,Nando satthu santikaṃ agantvā vanditvā paṭisanthāraṃ katvā satthāraṃ nimantetvā satthāhaṃ buddhappamukhassa bhikkhusaṅghassa paṇītaṃ pañcagorasadānaṃ adāsi. 
588081,122,954,88,97,1,81,9,Sattame divase satthā anumodanaṃ katvā dānakathādibhedaṃ anupubbiṃ kathaṃ kathesi. 
588082,122,954,98,121,1,162,17,"Kathāpariyosāne nandagopālako sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhāya satthu pattaṃ gahetvā satthāraṃ anugacchanto dūraṃ gantvā,‘‘ tiṭṭha, upāsakā’’ ti nivattiyamāno vanditvā nivatti. "
588083,122,954,122,128,1,37,6,Atha naṃ eko luddako vijjhitvā māresi. 
588084,122,954,129,138,1,61,8,Pacchato āgacchantā bhikkhū naṃ disvā gantvā satthāraṃ āhaṃsu–
588085,122,954,139,164,1,139,17,"‘‘ nando, bhante, gopālako tumhākaṃ idhāgatattā mahādānaṃ datvā anugantvā nivattento mārito, sace tumhe nāgacchissatha, nāssa maraṇaṃ abhavissā’’ ti. "
588086,122,954,165,186,1,125,16,"Satthā ,‘‘ bhikkhave, mayi āgatepi anāgatepi tassa catasso disā catasso anudisā ca gacchantassāpi maraṇato muccanūpāyo nāma natthi. "
588087,122,954,187,208,1,124,17,"Yañhi neva corā, na verino karonti, taṃ imesaṃ sattānaṃ antopaduṭṭhaṃ micchāpaṇihitaṃ cittameva karotī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
588088,122,955,2,4,1,0,0,42.
588089,122,956,2,14,1,46,10,"‘ ‘ Diso disaṃ yaṃ taṃ kayirā, verī vā pana verinaṃ; "
588090,122,957,2,12,1,46,7,"Micchāpaṇihitaṃ cittaṃ, pāpiyo naṃ tato kare’’ ti. "
588091,122,958,2,8,1,31,6,Tattha diso disan ti coro coraṃ.
588092,122,958,9,16,1,18,3,‘‘ Disvā’’ ti pāṭhaseso. 
588093,122,958,17,26,1,52,8,Yaṃ taṃ {kayirā}ti yaṃ taṃ tassa anayabyasanaṃ kareyya. 
588094,122,958,27,30,1,23,3,Dutiyapadepi eseva nayo. 
588095,122,958,31,97,1,478,59,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– eko ekassa mittadubbhī coro puttadārakhettavatthu gomahiṃsādīsu aparajjhanto yassa aparajjhati, tampi tatheva attani aparajjhantaṃ coraṃ disvā, veri vā pana kenacideva kāraṇena baddhaveraṃ veriṃ disvā attano kakkhaḷatāya dāruṇatāya yaṃ taṃ tassa anayabyasanaṃ kareyya, puttadāraṃ vā pīḷeyya, khettādīni vā nāseyya, jīvitā vā pana naṃ voropeyya, dasasu akusalakammapathesu micchāṭhapitattā micchāpahiṇitaṃ cittaṃ pāpiyo naṃ tato kare taṃ purisaṃ tato pāpataraṃ kareyya. "
588096,122,958,98,116,1,113,15,"Vuttappakārehi, diso disassa vā verī verino vā imasmiṃyeva attabhāve dukkhaṃ vā uppādeyya, jīvitakkhayaṃ vā kareyya. "
588097,122,958,117,135,1,164,17,"Idaṃ pana akusalakammapathesu micchāṭhapitaṃ cittaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme anayabyasanaṃ pāpeti, attabhāvasatasahassesupi catūsu apāyesu khipitvā sīsaṃ ukkhipituṃ na detīti. "
588098,122,959,2,7,1,46,4,Desanāpariyosāne bahū sotāpattiphalādīni pattā. 
588099,122,959,8,12,1,32,4,Mahājanassa sātthikā desanā jātā. 
588100,122,959,13,25,1,88,11,"Upāsakena pana bhavantare katakammaṃ bhikkhūhi na pucchitaṃ, tasmā satthārā na kathitanti. "
588101,122,960,2,4,1,28,2,Nandagopālakavatthu aṭṭhamaṃ.
588102,122,961,2,4,1,19,2,9 . Soreyyattheravatthu 
588103,122,962,2,18,1,113,14,Na taṃ mātā pitā {kayirā}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā sāvatthiyaṃ jetavane viharanto soreyyattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
588104,122,963,2,8,1,55,5,"Vatthu soreyyanagare samuṭṭhitaṃ, sāvatthiyaṃ niṭṭhāpesi. "
588105,122,963,9,24,1,165,15,Sammāsambuddhe sāvatthiyaṃ viharante soreyyanagare soreyyaseṭṭhiputto ekena sahāyakena saddhiṃ sukhayānake nisīditvā mahantena parivārena nhānatthāya nagarā nikkhami. 
588106,122,963,25,35,1,104,10,Tasmiṃ khaṇe mahākaccāyanatthero soreyyanagaraṃ piṇḍāya pavisitukāmo hutvā bahinagare saṅghāṭiṃ pārupati. 
588107,122,963,36,40,1,33,4,Therassa ca suvaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ sarīraṃ. 
588108,122,963,41,45,1,36,4,Soreyyaseṭṭhiputto taṃ disvā cintesi–
588109,122,963,46,69,1,110,17,"‘‘ aho vata ayaṃ vā thero mama bhariyā bhaveyya, mama vā bhariyāya sarīravaṇṇo etassa sarīravaṇṇo viya bhaveyyā’’ ti. "
588110,122,963,70,77,1,70,6,"Tassa cintitamatteyeva purisaliṅgaṃ antaradhāyi, itthiliṅgaṃ pāturahosi. "
588111,122,963,78,83,1,33,5,So lajjamāno yānakā oruyha palāyi. 
588112,122,963,84,94,1,39,6,Parijano taṃ asañjānanto‘‘ kimetan’’ ti āha. 
588113,122,963,95,98,1,30,3,Sāpi takkasilamaggaṃ paṭipajji. 
588114,122,963,99,105,1,45,6,Sahāyakopissā ito cito ca vicaritvāpi nāddasa. 
588115,122,963,106,110,1,29,4,Sabbe nhāyitvā gehaṃ agamiṃsu.
588116,122,963,111,131,1,75,11,"‘‘ Kahaṃ seṭṭhiputto’’ ti ca vutte,‘‘ nhatvā āgato bhavissatīti maññimhā’’ ti vadiṃsu. "
588117,122,963,132,150,1,114,13,"Athassa mātāpitaro tattha tattha pariyesitvā apassantā roditvā paridevitvā,‘‘ mato bhavissatī’’ ti matakabhattaṃ adaṃsu. "
588118,122,963,151,160,1,78,9,Sā ekaṃ takkasilagāmiṃ satthavāhaṃ disvā yānakassa pacchato pacchato anubandhi. 
588119,122,964,2,28,1,119,18,"Atha naṃ manussā disvā,‘‘ amhākaṃ yānakassa pacchato pacchato anugacchati, mayaṃ‘ kassesā dārikā’ ti taṃ na jānāmā’’ ti vadiṃsu. "
588120,122,964,29,50,1,118,16,"Sāpi‘‘ tumhe attano yānakaṃ pājetha, ahaṃ padasā gamissāmī’’ ti gacchantī aṅgulimuddikaṃ datvā ekasmiṃ yānake okāsaṃ kāresi. "
588121,122,964,51,53,1,18,2,Manussā cintayiṃsu–
588122,122,964,54,71,1,103,11,"‘‘ takkasilanagare amhākaṃ seṭṭhiputtassa bhariyā natthi, tassa ācikkhissāma, mahāpaṇṇākāro no bhavissatī’’ ti. "
588123,122,964,72,90,1,71,11,"Te gehaṃ gantvā,‘‘ sāmi, amhehi tumhākaṃ ekaṃ itthiratanaṃ ānītan’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
588124,122,964,91,105,1,99,13,So taṃ sutvā taṃ pakkosāpetvā attano vayānurūpaṃ abhirūpaṃ pāsādikaṃ disvā uppannasineho gehe akāsi. 
588125,122,964,106,117,1,59,9,"Purisā hi itthiyo, itthiyo vā purisā abhūtapubbā nāma natthi. "
588126,122,964,118,134,1,149,16,Purisā hi parassa dāresu aticaritvā kālaṃ katvā bahūni vassasatasahassāni niraye paccitvā manussajātiṃ āgacchantā attabhāvasate itthibhāvaṃ āpajjanti. 
588127,122,965,2,12,1,115,10,Ānandattheropi kappasatasahassaṃ pūritapāramī ariyasāvako saṃsāre saṃsaranto ekasmiṃ attabhāve kammārakule nibbatto. 
588128,122,965,13,29,1,150,15,"Paradārakammaṃ katvā niraye paccitvā pakkāvasesena cuddasasu attabhāvesu purisassa pādaparicārikā itthī ahosi, sattasu attabhāvesu bījuddharaṇaṃ pāpuṇi. "
588129,122,965,30,62,1,259,26,"Itthiyo pana dānādīni puññāni katvā itthibhāve chandaṃ virājetvā,‘‘ idaṃ no puññaṃ purisattabhāvapaṭilābhāya saṃvattatū’’ ti cittaṃ adhiṭṭhahitvā kālaṃ katvā purisattabhāvaṃ paṭilabhanti, patidevatā hutvā sāmike sammāpaṭipattivasenāpi purisattabhāvaṃ paṭilabhanteva. "
588130,122,966,2,13,1,96,11,Ayaṃ pana seṭṭhiputto there ayoniso cittaṃ uppādetvā imasmiṃyeva attabhāve itthibhāvaṃ paṭilabhi. 
588131,122,966,14,23,1,88,9,Takkasilāyaṃ seṭṭhiputtena saddhiṃ saṃvāsamanvāya pana tassā kucchiyaṃ gabbho patiṭṭhāsi. 
588132,122,966,24,34,1,84,10,Sā dasamāsaccayena puttaṃ labhitvā tassa padasā gamanakāle aparampi puttaṃ paṭilabhi. 
588133,122,966,35,48,1,91,12,"Evamassā kucchiyaṃ vutthā dve, soreyyanagare taṃ paṭicca nibbattā dveti cattāro puttā ahesuṃ. "
588134,122,966,49,64,1,128,14,Tasmiṃ kāle soreyyanagarato tassā sahāyako seṭṭhiputto pañcahi sakaṭasatehi takkasilaṃ gantvā sukhayānake nisinno nagaraṃ pāvisi. 
588135,122,966,65,84,1,174,19,Atha naṃ sā uparipāsādatale vātapānaṃ vivaritvā antaravīthiṃ olokayamānā ṭhitā disvā sañjānitvā dāsiṃ pesetvā pakkosāpetvā mahātale nisīdāpetvā mahantaṃ sakkārasammānaṃ akāsi. 
588136,122,966,85,89,1,15,4,Atha naṃ so āha–
588137,122,966,90,115,1,104,18,"‘‘ bhadde, tvaṃ ito pubbe amhehi na diṭṭhapubbā, atha ca pana no mahantaṃ sakkāraṃ karosi, jānāsi tvaṃ amhe’’ ti."
588138,122,966,116,130,1,49,7,"‘‘ Āma, sāmi, jānāmi, nanu tumhe soreyyanagaravāsino’’ ti?"
588139,122,966,131,139,1,13,3,"‘‘ Āma, bhadde’’ ti. "
588140,122,966,140,147,1,59,7,Sā mātāpitūnañca bhariyāya ca puttānañca arogabhāvaṃ pucchi. 
588141,122,966,148,169,1,54,11,"Itaro‘‘ āma, bhadde, arogā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ jānāsi tvaṃ ete’’ ti āha."
588142,122,966,170,176,1,15,3,"‘‘ Āma sāmi, jānāmi. "
588143,122,966,177,189,1,38,8,"Tesaṃ eko putto atthi, so kahaṃ, sāmī’’ ti?"
588144,122,966,190,228,1,217,29,"‘‘ Bhadde, mā etaṃ kathehi, mayaṃ tena saddhiṃ ekadivasaṃ sukhayānake nisīditvā nhāyituṃ nikkhantā nevassa gatiṃ jānāma, ito cito ca vicaritvā taṃ adisvā mātāpitūnaṃ ārocayimhā, tepissa roditvā kanditvā petakiccaṃ kiriṃsū’’ ti."
588145,122,966,229,238,1,15,4,"‘‘ Ahaṃ so, sāmī’’ ti."
588146,122,966,239,256,1,68,11,"‘‘ Apehi, bhadde, kiṃ kathesi mayhaṃ sahāyo devakumāro viya eko puriso’’ ti?"
588147,122,966,257,268,1,20,5,"‘‘ Hotu, sāmi, ahaṃ so’’ ti."
588148,122,966,269,278,1,21,5,‘‘ Atha idaṃ kiṃ nāmā’’ ti?
588149,122,966,279,290,1,49,7,‘‘ Taṃ divasaṃ te ayyo mahākaccāyanatthero diṭṭho’’ ti?
588150,122,966,291,299,1,13,3,"‘‘ Āma, diṭṭho’’ ti. "
588151,122,966,300,330,1,160,22,"Ahaṃ ayyaṃ mahākaccāyanattheraṃ oloketvā,‘‘ aho vata ayaṃ vā thero mama bhariyā bhaveyya , etassa vā sarīravaṇṇo viya mama bhariyāya sarīravaṇṇo bhaveyyā’’ ti cintesiṃ. "
588152,122,966,331,338,1,67,6,"Cintitakkhaṇeyeva me purisaliṅgaṃ antaradhāyi, itthiliṅgaṃ pātubhavi. "
