588154,122,967,2,23,1,88,16,"‘ ‘ Aho vata te bhāriyaṃ kammaṃ kataṃ, kasmā mayhaṃ nācikkhi, apica pana te thero khamāpito’’ ti?"
588155,122,967,24,30,1,17,3,"‘‘ Na khamāpito, sāmi. "
