588157,122,967,40,49,1,38,5,‘‘ Imameva nagaraṃ upanissāya viharatī’’ ti.
588158,122,967,50,67,1,82,11,"‘‘ Sace piṇḍāya caranto idhāgaccheyya, ahaṃ mama ayyassa bhikkhāhāraṃ dadeyyaṃ, sāmī’’ ti."
588159,122,967,68,102,1,163,23,"‘‘ Tena hi sīghaṃ sakkāraṃ karohi, amhākaṃ ayyaṃ khamāpessāmā’’ ti so therassa vasanaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisinno,‘‘ bhante, sve mayhaṃ bhikkhaṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti āha."
