588162,122,967,132,139,1,54,6,"Thero adhivāsesi, gehepi therassa mahāsakkāro paṭiyatto. "
588163,122,967,140,145,1,39,5,Thero punadivase taṃ gehadvāraṃ agamāsi. 
588164,122,967,146,170,1,150,18,"Atha naṃ nisīdāpetvā paṇītenāhārena parivisitvā seṭṭhiputto taṃ itthiṃ gahetvā therassa pādamūle nipajjāpetvā,‘‘ bhante, mayhaṃ sahāyikāya khamathā’’ ti āha."
588165,122,967,171,177,1,10,2,‘‘ Kimetan’’ ti?
588166,122,967,178,207,1,150,19,"‘‘ Ayaṃ, bhante, pubbe mayhaṃ piyasahāyako hutvā tumhe oloketvā evaṃ nāma cintesi, athassa purisaliṅgaṃ antaradhāyi, itthiliṅgaṃ pātubhavi, khamatha, bhante’’ ti."
588167,122,967,208,220,1,37,7,"‘‘ Tena hi uṭṭhahatha, khamāmi vo ahan’’ ti. "
588168,122,967,221,235,1,80,8,"Therena ‘‘ khamāmī’’ ti vuttamatteyeva itthiliṅgaṃ antaradhāyi, purisaliṅgaṃ pātubhavi. "
588169,122,968,2,8,1,62,6,Purisaliṅge pātubhūtamatteyeva taṃ takkasilāya seṭṭhiputto āha–
588170,122,968,9,35,1,133,19,"‘‘ samma sahāyaka, ime dve dārakā tava kucchiyaṃ vutthattā maṃ paṭicca nibbattattā ubhinnampino puttā eva, idheva vasissāma, mā ukkaṇṭhī’’ ti."
588171,122,968,36,86,1,295,39,"‘‘ Samma, ahaṃ ekenattabhāvena paṭhamaṃ puriso hutvā itthibhāvaṃ patvā puna puriso jātoti vippakārappatto, paṭhamaṃ maṃ paṭicca dve puttā nibbattā, idāni me kucchito dve puttā nikkhantā, svāhaṃ ekenattabhāvena vippakārappatto, puna‘ gehe vasissatī’ ti saññaṃ mā kari, ahaṃ mama ayyassa santike pabbajissāmi. "
588172,122,968,87,113,1,167,23,"Ime dve dārakā tava bhārāti, imesu mā pamajjī’’ ti vatvā putte sīse paricumbitvā parimajjitvā ure nipajjāpetvā pitu niyyādetvā nikkhamitvā therassa santike pabbajjaṃ yāci. "
588173,122,968,114,124,1,93,10,Theropi naṃ pabbājetvā upasampādetvā gaṇhitvāva cārikaṃ caramāno anupubbena sāvatthiṃ agamāsi. 
588174,122,968,125,130,1,33,4,Tassa {soreyyatthero}ti nāmaṃ ahosi. 
588175,122,968,131,141,1,87,9,Janapadavāsino taṃ pavattiṃ ñatvā saṅkhubhitvā kotūhalajātā taṃ upasaṅkamitvā pucchiṃsu –
588176,122,968,142,151,1,19,4,"‘‘ evaṃ kira, bhante’’ ti?"
588177,122,968,152,160,1,12,3,"‘‘ Āma, āvuso’’ ti."
588178,122,968,161,171,1,35,5,"‘‘ Bhante, evarūpampi kāraṇaṃ nāma hoti’’?"
588179,122,968,172,195,1,104,16,"‘‘ Tumhākaṃ kucchiyaṃ kira dve puttā nibbattā, tumhe paṭicca dve jātā, tesaṃ vo kataresu balavasineho hotī’’ ti?"
588180,122,968,196,205,1,29,4,"‘‘ Kucchiyaṃ vutthakesu, āvuso’’ ti. "
588181,122,968,206,210,1,37,4,Āgatāgatā nibaddhaṃ tatheva pucchiṃsu. 
588182,122,969,2,21,1,107,14,"Thero ‘‘ kucchiyaṃ vuttakesu eva sineho balavā’’ ti punappunaṃ kathento harāyamāno ekova nisīdati, ekova tiṭṭhati. "
588183,122,969,22,32,1,92,10,So evaṃ ekattūpagato attabhāve khayavayaṃ samuṭṭhāpetvā saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
588184,122,969,33,37,1,28,4,Atha naṃ āgatāgatā pucchanti–
588185,122,969,38,49,1,30,6,"‘‘ bhante, evaṃ kira nāma ahosī’’ ti?"
588186,122,969,50,56,1,10,2,‘‘ Āmāvuso’’ ti.
588187,122,969,57,65,1,25,4,‘‘ Kataresu sineho balavā’’ ti?
588188,122,969,66,76,1,37,6,‘‘ Mayhaṃ katthaci sineho nāma natthī’’ ti. 
588189,122,969,77,111,1,169,23,"Bhikkhū‘‘ ayaṃ abhūtaṃ kathesi, purimadivasesu‘ kucchiyaṃ vutthaputtesu sineho balavā’ ti vatvā idāni‘ mayhaṃ katthaci sineho natthī’ ti vadati, aññaṃ byākaroti, bhante’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
588190,122,969,112,160,1,279,38,"Satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, mama putto aññaṃ byākaroti, mama puttassa sammāpaṇihitena cittena maggassa diṭṭhakālato paṭṭhāya na katthaci sineho jāto, yaṃ sampattiṃ neva mātā, na pitā kātuṃ sakkoti, taṃ imesaṃ sattānaṃ abbhantare pavattaṃ sammāpaṇihitaṃ cittameva detī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
588191,122,970,2,4,1,0,0,43.
588192,122,971,2,15,1,43,10,"‘ ‘ Na taṃ mātā pitā kayirā, aññe vāpi ca ñātakā; "
588193,122,972,2,12,1,46,7,"Sammāpaṇihitaṃ cittaṃ, seyyaso naṃ tato kare’’ ti. "
588194,122,973,2,18,1,69,14,"Tattha na tan ti taṃ kāraṇaṃ neva mātā kareyya, na pitā, na aññe ñātakā. "
588195,122,973,19,25,1,58,6,Sammāpaṇihitan ti dasasu kusalakammapathesu sammā ṭhapitaṃ. 
588196,122,973,26,42,1,94,13,"Seyyaso naṃ tato {kare}ti tato kāraṇato seyyaso naṃ varataraṃ uttaritaraṃ kareyya, karotīti attho. "
588197,122,973,43,57,1,119,14,Mātāpitaro hi puttānaṃ dhanaṃ dadamānā ekasmiṃyeva attabhāve kammaṃ akatvā sukhena jīvikakappanaṃ dhanaṃ dātuṃ sakkonti. 
588198,122,973,58,71,1,113,12,"Visākhāya mātāpitaropi tāva mahaddhanā mahābhogā, tassā ekasmiṃyeva attabhāve sukhena jīvikakappanaṃ dhanaṃ adaṃsu. "
588199,122,973,72,100,1,236,25,"Catūsu pana dīpesu cakkavattisiriṃ dātuṃ samatthā mātāpitaropi nāma puttānaṃ natthi, pageva dibbasampattiṃ vā paṭhamajjhānādisampattiṃ vā, lokuttarasampattidāne kathāva natthi, sammāpaṇihitaṃ pana cittaṃ sabbampetaṃ sampattiṃ dātuṃ sakkoti. "
588200,122,973,101,112,1,36,7,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ seyyaso naṃ tato kare’’ ti. 
