588705,122,1082,237,273,1,170,25,"So ājīvakassa vacanaṃ sutvā satthu santikaṃ gantvā nimantetvā ājīvakena vuttaniyāmeneva sabbaṃ katvā tassa santikaṃ gantvā,‘‘ kiṃ te katan’’ ti puṭṭho,‘‘ sabbaṃ kataṃ, ayyā’’ ti āha."
588706,122,1082,274,294,1,104,15,"‘‘ Bhaddakaṃ te kataṃ, tassa sakkāraṃ ubhopi khādissāmā’’ ti vatvā punadivase ājīvako pātova taṃ gehaṃ agamāsi. "
588707,122,1082,295,299,1,36,4,Taṃ gahetvā pacchāgabbhe nisīdāpesuṃ. 
588708,122,1083,2,16,1,136,13,Paṭivissakamanussā taṃ gehaṃ allagomayena upalimpitvā lājapañcamāni pupphāni vikiritvā satthu nisīdanatthāya mahārahaṃ āsanaṃ paññāpesuṃ. 
588709,122,1083,17,65,1,330,37,"Buddhehi saddhiṃ aparicitamanussā hi āsanapaññattiṃ na jānanti, buddhānañca maggadesakena kiccaṃ nāma natthi, bodhimūle dasasahassisokadhātuṃ kampetvā sambodhiṃ pattadivaseyeva hi nesaṃ‘‘ ayaṃ maggo nirayaṃ gacchati, ayaṃ tiracchānayoniṃ, ayaṃ pettivisayaṃ, ayaṃ manussalokaṃ, ayaṃ devalokaṃ, ayaṃ amatamahānibbānan’’ ti sabbe maggā āvibhūtā. "
