588742,122,1092,131,150,1,96,15,"Rājānaṃ disvā uṭṭhahantena hi rājā garukato hoti, no satthā, tasmā neva uṭṭhahissāmī’’ ti na uṭṭhahi. "
588743,122,1092,151,160,1,81,9,Paṇḍitapurisā nāma garutarānaṃ santike nisīditvā anuṭṭhahantaṃ disvā na kujjhanti. 
588744,122,1092,161,171,1,82,10,Rājā pana taṃ anuṭṭhahantaṃ disvā kupitamānaso satthāraṃ vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
588745,122,1092,172,193,1,139,15,"Satthā kupitabhāvaṃ ñatvā,‘‘ mahārāja, ayaṃ chattapāṇi upāsako paṇḍito diṭṭhadhammo tipiṭakadharo atthānatthakusalo’’ ti upāsakassa guṇaṃ kathesi. "
588746,122,1092,194,201,1,56,7,Rañño tassa guṇakathaṃ suṇantasseva cittaṃ mudukaṃ jātaṃ. 
