588796,122,1104,2,4,1,13,2,8 . Visākhāvatthu 
588797,122,1105,2,17,1,126,13,Yathāpi {puppharāsimhā}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā sāvatthiyaṃ upanissāya pubbārāme viharanto visākhaṃ upāsikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
588798,122,1106,2,13,1,120,10,Sā kira aṅgaraṭṭhe bhaddiyanagare meṇḍakaseṭṭhiputtassa dhanañcayaseṭṭhino aggamahesiyā sumanadeviyā kucchismiṃ nibbatti. 
588799,122,1106,14,27,1,156,13,Tassā sattavassikakāle satthā selabrāhmaṇādīnaṃ bodhaneyyabandhavānaṃ upanissayasampadaṃ disvā mahābhikkhusaṅghaparivāro cārikaṃ caramāno taṃ nagaraṃ pāpuṇi. 
588800,122,1107,2,17,1,105,12,"Tasmiñca samaye meṇḍako, gahapati, tasmiṃ nagare pañcannaṃ mahāpuññānaṃ jeṭṭhako hutvā seṭṭhiṭṭhānaṃ karoti. "
588801,122,1107,18,43,1,178,21,"Pañca mahāpuññā nāma meṇḍako seṭṭhi, candapadumā nāma tasseva jeṭṭhakabhariyā, tasseva jeṭṭhakaputto dhanañcayo nāma, tassa bhariyā sumanadevī nāma, meṇḍakaseṭṭhino dāso puṇṇo nāmāti. "
588802,122,1107,44,65,1,129,15,"Na kevalañca meṇḍakaseṭṭhiyeva, bimbisārarañño pana vijite pañca amitabhogā nāma ahesuṃ– jotiko, jaṭilo, meṇḍako, puṇṇako, kākavaliyoti. "
588803,122,1107,66,81,1,142,15,Tesu ayaṃ meṇḍakaseṭṭhi dasabalassa attano nagaraṃ sampattabhāvaṃ ñatvā puttassa dhanañcayaseṭṭhino dhītaraṃ visākhaṃ dārikaṃ pakkosāpetvā āha–
588804,122,1107,82,109,1,175,20,"‘‘ amma, tuyhampi maṅgalaṃ, amhākampi maṅgalaṃ, tava parivārehi pañcahi dārikāsatehi saddhiṃ pañca rathasatāni āruyha pañcahi dāsisatehi parivutā dasabalassa paccuggamanaṃ karohī’’ ti. "
588805,122,1107,110,120,1,36,6,Sā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā tathā akāsi. 
588806,122,1107,121,138,1,145,16,"Kāraṇākāraṇesu pana kusalattā yāvatikā yānassa bhūmi, yānena gantvā yānā paccorohitvā pattikāva satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. "
588807,122,1107,139,144,1,42,5,Athassā cariyāvasena satthā dhammaṃ desesi. 
588808,122,1107,145,152,1,70,7,Sā desanāvasāne pañcahi dārikāsatehi saddhiṃ sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi. 
588809,122,1107,153,175,1,253,22,Meṇḍakaseṭṭhipi kho satthāramupasaṅkamitvā dhammakathaṃ sutvā sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhāya svātanāya nimantetvā punadivase attano nivesane paṇītena khādanīyena bhojanīyena buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ parivisitvā eteneva upāyena aḍḍhamāsaṃ mahādānamadāsi. 
588810,122,1107,176,181,1,54,5,Satthā bhaddiyanagare yathābhirantaṃ viharitvā pakkāmi. 
