588822,122,1108,210,226,1,120,15,"So taṃ ādāya sabbattha ekarattivāsena gacchanto ekaṃ phāsukaṭṭhānaṃ patvā nivāsaṃ gaṇhi, atha naṃ dhanañcayaseṭṭhi pucchi–"
