588834,122,1109,55,72,1,108,13,So punappunaṃ vuccamāno‘‘ tena hi pañcakalyāṇasamannāgataṃ dārikaṃ labhamāno tumhākaṃ vacanaṃ karissāmī’’ ti āha.
