588840,122,1109,202,243,1,246,30,"‘‘ Tena hi evarūpaṃ dārikaṃ pariyesituṃ aṭṭha janā gacchantū’’ ti bahuṃ dhanaṃ datvā‘‘ āgatakāle vo kattabbaṃ jānissāma, gacchatha, evarūpaṃ dārikaṃ pariyesatha, diṭṭhakāle ca imaṃ pilandhanaṃ dadeyyāthā’’ ti satasahassagghanikaṃ suvaṇṇamālaṃ datvā uyyojesuṃ. "
