589228,122,1174,28,41,1,65,10,"Atthi nu kho taṃ gandhajātaṃ, yassa paṭivātampi gandho gacchatī’’ ti. "
589229,122,1174,42,44,1,17,2,Athassa etadahosi–
589230,122,1174,45,57,1,59,7,"‘‘ kiṃ mayhaṃ attanā vinicchitena, satthāraṃyeva pucchissāmī’’ ti. "
589231,122,1174,58,62,1,33,4,So satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā pucchi. 
589232,122,1174,63,65,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
589233,122,1175,2,30,1,197,23,"‘ ‘ Atha kho āyasmā ānando sāyanhasamaye paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami , upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi, ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–"
589234,122,1176,2,17,1,75,10,"‘ ‘ Tīṇimāni, bhante, gandhajātāni, yesaṃ anuvātameva gandho gacchati, no paṭivātaṃ. "
589235,122,1176,18,20,1,13,2,Katamāni tīṇi? 
