589268,122,1193,2,4,1,37,2,10 . Mahākassapattherapiṇḍapātadinnavatthu 
589269,122,1194,2,17,1,120,12,Appamatto ayaṃ {gandho}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto mahākassapattherassa piṇḍapātadānaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
589270,122,1195,2,18,1,103,12,Ekasmiñhi divase thero sattāhaccayena nirodhā vuṭṭhāya‘‘ rājagahe sapadānaṃ piṇḍāya carissāmī’’ ti nikkhami. 
589271,122,1195,19,59,1,244,29,"Tasmiṃ pana samaye sakkassa devarañño paricārikā kakuṭapādiniyo pañcasatā accharāyo‘‘ therassa piṇḍapātaṃ dassāmā’’ ti ussāhajātā pañca piṇḍapātasatāni sajjetvā ādāya antarāmagge ṭhatvā,‘‘ bhante, imaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ gaṇhatha, saṅgahaṃ no karothā’’ ti vadiṃsu."
589272,122,1195,60,72,1,53,7,"‘‘ Gacchatha tumhe, ahaṃ duggatānaṃ saṅgahaṃ karissāmī’’ ti."
589273,122,1195,73,87,1,43,8,"‘‘ Bhante, mā no nāsetha, saṅgahaṃ no karothā’’ ti. "
589274,122,1195,88,110,1,127,16,"Thero ñatvā puna paṭikkhipitvā punapi apagantuṃ anicchamānā yācantiyo‘‘ attano pamāṇaṃ na jānātha, apagacchathā’’ ti accharaṃ pahari. "
589275,122,1195,111,149,1,207,25,"Tā therassa accharasaddaṃ sutvā santhambhitvā sammukhā ṭhātuṃ asakkontiyo palāyitvā devalokameva gantvā, sakkena‘‘ kahaṃ gatātthā’’ ti puṭṭhā,‘‘‘ samāpattito vuṭṭhitassa therassa piṇḍapātaṃ dassāmā’ ti gatāmhā, devā’’ ti."
589276,122,1195,150,158,1,16,4,‘‘ Dinno pana vā’’ ti?
589277,122,1195,159,167,1,22,4,‘‘ Gaṇhituṃ na icchatī’’ ti.
589278,122,1195,168,175,1,14,3,‘‘ Kiṃ kathesī’’ ti?
589279,122,1195,176,190,1,44,7,"‘‘‘ Duggatānaṃ saṅgahaṃ karissāmī’ ti āha, devā’’ ti."
589280,122,1195,191,199,1,24,4,‘‘ Tumhe kenākārena gatā’’ ti.
589281,122,1195,200,208,1,15,3,"‘‘ Imināva, devā’’ ti. "
589282,122,1195,209,243,1,259,29,"Sakko‘‘ tumhādisiyo therassa piṇḍapātaṃ kiṃ dassantī’’ ti sayaṃ dātukāmo hutvā, jarājiṇṇo mahallako khaṇḍadanto palitakeso otaggasarīro mahallakatanta vāyo hutvā sujampi devadhītaraṃ tathārūpameva mahallikaṃ katvā ekaṃ pesakāravīthiṃ māpetvā tantaṃ pasārento acchi. "
589283,122,1196,2,22,1,122,16,Theropi ‘‘ duggatānaṃ saṅgahaṃ karissāmī’’ ti nagarābhimukho gacchanto bahinagare eva taṃ vīthiṃ disvā olokento dve jane addasa. 
589284,122,1196,23,32,1,55,8,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe sakko tantaṃ pasāreti, sujā tasaraṃ vaṭṭeti. "
589285,122,1196,33,35,1,13,2,Thero cintesi–
589286,122,1196,36,61,1,162,19,"‘‘ ime mahallakakālepi kammaṃ karontiyeva imasmiṃ nagare imehi duggatatarā natthi maññe, imehi dinnaṃ uḷuṅkamattampi sākamattampi gahetvā imesaṃ saṅgahaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
589287,122,1196,62,66,1,27,4,So tesaṃ gehābhimukho ahosi. 
589288,122,1196,67,73,1,37,6,Sakko taṃ āgacchantaṃ disvā sujaṃ āha–
589289,122,1196,74,98,1,117,17,"‘‘ bhadde, mayhaṃ ayyo ito āgacchati, tvaṃ apassantī viya tuṇhī hutvā nisīda, khaṇena theraṃ vañcetvā piṇḍapātaṃ dassāmā’’ ti. "
589290,122,1196,99,104,1,31,4,Thero āgantvā gehadvāre aṭṭhāsi. 
589291,122,1196,105,113,1,60,8,Tepi apassantā viya attano kammameva karontā thokaṃ āgamiṃsu. 
589292,122,1197,2,19,1,64,11,"Atha sakko‘‘ gehadvāre eko thero viya ṭhito, upadhārehi tāvā’’ ti āha."
589293,122,1197,20,29,1,26,4,"‘‘ Gantvā upadhāretha, sāmī’’ ti. "
589294,122,1197,30,90,1,323,46,"So gehā nikkhamitvā theraṃ pañcapatiṭṭhitena vanditvā ubhohi hatthehi jaṇṇukāni olambitvā nitthunanto uṭṭhāya‘‘ kataro thero nu kho ayyo’’ ti thokaṃ osakkitvā‘‘ akkhīni me dhūmāyantī’’ ti vatvā nalāṭe hatthaṃ ṭhapetvā uddhaṃ oloketvā‘‘ aho dukkhaṃ, ayyo no mahākassapatthero cirassaṃ me kuṭidvāraṃ āgato, atthi nu kho kiñci gehe’’ ti āha. "
589295,122,1197,91,106,1,61,10,"Sujā thokaṃ ākulaṃ viya hutvā‘‘ atthi, sāmī’’ ti paṭivacanaṃ adāsi. "
589296,122,1197,107,126,1,81,13,"Sakko,‘‘ bhante, lūkhaṃ vā paṇītaṃ vāti acintetvā saṅgahaṃ no karothā’’ ti pattaṃ gaṇhi. "
589297,122,1197,127,147,1,90,14,"Thero‘‘ etehi dinnaṃ sākaṃ vā hotu kuṇḍakamuṭṭhi vā, saṅgahaṃ nesaṃ karissāmī’’ ti pattaṃ adāsi. "
589298,122,1197,148,160,1,98,12,So antogharaṃ pavisitvā ghaṭiodanaṃ nāma ghaṭiyā uddharitvā pattaṃ pūretvā therassa hatthe ṭhapesi. 
589299,122,1197,161,170,1,81,8,"So ahosi piṇḍapāto anekasūpabyañjano, sakalaṃ rājagahanagaraṃ gandhena ajjhotthari. "
