589314,122,1198,236,238,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
589315,122,1199,2,11,1,63,8,‘ ‘ Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. 
589316,122,1199,12,29,1,133,15,"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā mahākassapo pippaliguhāyaṃ viharati, sattāhaṃ ekapallaṅkena nisinno hoti aññataraṃ samādhiṃ samāpajjitvā. "
589317,122,1199,30,40,1,79,10,Atha kho āyasmā mahākassapo tassa sattāhassa accayena tamhā samādhimhā vuṭṭhāsi. 
589318,122,1199,41,49,1,71,8,Atha kho āyasmato mahākassapassa tamhā samādhimhā vuṭṭhitassa etadahosi–
589319,122,1199,50,59,1,42,5,‘‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ rājagahaṃ piṇḍāya paviseyyan’’ ti.
589320,122,1200,2,16,1,117,13,‘ ‘ Tena kho pana samayena pañcamattāni devatāsatāni ussukkaṃ āpannāni honti āyasmato mahākassapassa piṇḍapātapaṭilābhāya. 
589321,122,1200,17,32,1,141,14,Atha kho āyasmā mahākassapo tāni pañcamattāni devatāsatāni paṭikkhipitvā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya rājagahaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi.
589322,122,1201,2,15,1,89,12,‘ ‘ Tena kho pana samayena sakko devānamindo āyasmato mahākassapassa piṇḍapātaṃ dātukāmo hoti. 
589323,122,1201,16,25,1,74,8,"Pesakāravaṇṇaṃ abhinimminitvā tantaṃ vināti, sujā asurakaññā tasaraṃ pūreti. "
589324,122,1201,26,66,1,339,38,"Atha kho āyasmā mahākassapo rājagahe sapadānaṃ piṇḍāya caramāno yena sakkassa devānamindassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami, addasā kho sakko devānamindo āyasmantaṃ mahākassapaṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ, disvā gharā nikkhamitvā paccuggantvā hatthato pattaṃ gahetvā gharaṃ pavisitvā ghaṭiyā odanaṃ uddharitvā pattaṃ pūretvā āyasmato mahākassapassa adāsi. "
589325,122,1201,67,73,1,60,6,So ahosi piṇḍapāto anekasūpo anekabyañjano anekarasabyañjano. 
589326,122,1201,74,79,1,42,5,Atha kho āyasmato mahākassapassa etadahosi–
589327,122,1201,80,92,1,53,9,"‘ ko nu kho ayaṃ satto, yassāyaṃ evarūpo iddhānubhāvo’ ti. "
589328,122,1201,93,99,1,42,5,Atha kho āyasmato mahākassapassa etadahosi–
589329,122,1201,100,111,1,67,9,‘ sakko kho ayaṃ devānamindo’ ti viditvā sakkaṃ devānamindaṃ etadavoca–
589330,122,1201,112,128,1,51,9,"‘ kataṃ kho te idaṃ, kosiya, mā punapi evarūpamakāsī’’’ ti."
589331,122,1201,129,145,1,69,9,"‘‘ Amhākampi, bhante kassapa, puññena attho, amhākampi puññena karaṇīyan’’ ti."
589332,122,1202,2,20,1,144,17,‘ ‘ Atha kho sakko devānamindo āyasmantaṃ mahākassapaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā vehāsaṃ abbhuggantvā ākāse antalikkhe tikkhattuṃ udānaṃ udānesi–
589333,122,1202,21,48,1,137,16,"‘ aho dānaṃ paramadānaṃ kassape suppatiṭṭhitaṃ, aho dānaṃ paramadānaṃ kassape suppatiṭṭhitaṃ, aho dānaṃ paramadānaṃ kassape suppatiṭṭhitan’’’ ti( udā.27). "
589334,122,1203,2,14,1,74,12,Atha kho bhagavā vihāre ṭhito eva tassa taṃ saddaṃ sutvā bhikkhū āmantetvā–
589335,122,1203,15,32,1,80,10,"‘‘ passatha , bhikkhave, sakkaṃ devānamindaṃ udānaṃ udānetvā ākāsena gacchantan’’ ti āha."
589336,122,1203,33,44,1,29,6,"‘‘ Kiṃ pana tena kataṃ, bhante’’ ti?"
589337,122,1203,45,64,1,107,14,"‘‘ Vañcetvā tena mayhaṃ puttassa kassapassa piṇḍapāto dinno, taṃ datvā tuṭṭhamānaso udānaṃ udānento gacchatī’’ ti."
589338,122,1203,65,80,1,63,9,"‘‘ Therassa piṇḍapātaṃ dātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti kathaṃ, bhante, tena ñātanti."
