589680,122,1294,19,25,1,43,6,Rañño taṃ desanaṃ sutvā mahāsaṃvego uppajji. 
589681,122,1294,26,77,1,351,43,"So‘‘ bhāriyaṃ vatidaṃ pāradārikakammaṃ nāma, ekaṃ kira buddhantaraṃ niraye paccitvā tato cutā saṭṭhiyojanikāya lohakumbhiyā nibbattitvā tattha saṭṭhivassasahassāni paccitvā evampi nesaṃ dukkhā muccanakālo na paññāyati, ahampi paradāre sinehaṃ katvā sabbarattiṃ niddaṃ na labhiṃ, idāni ito paṭṭhāya paradāre mānasaṃ na bandhissāmī’’ ti cintetvā tathāgataṃ āha–"
589682,122,1294,78,90,1,41,7,"‘‘ bhante, ajja me rattiyā dīghabhāvo ñāto’’ ti. "
