589685,122,1294,131,161,1,164,23,"Satthā dvinnampi kathaṃ saṃsanditvā‘‘ ekaccassa ratti dīghā hoti, ekaccassa yojanaṃ dīghaṃ hoti, bālassa pana saṃsāro dīgho hotī’’ ti vatvā dhammaṃ desento imaṃ gāthamāha– "
