589786,122,1320,22,53,1,180,22,"Atheko bhikkhu aparabhāge rājagahā nikkhamitvā satthāraṃ daṭṭhukāmo jetavanaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā satthārā paṭisanthāraṃ katvā‘‘ kuto āgatosī’’ ti puṭṭho‘‘ rājagahato, bhante’’ ti āha."
