589825,122,1341,2,14,1,92,10,Puttā {matthī}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā sāvatthiyaṃ viharanto ānandaseṭṭhiṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
589826,122,1342,2,9,1,74,7,Sāvatthiyaṃ kira ānandaseṭṭhi nāma cattālīsakoṭivibhavo mahāmaccharī ahosi. 
589827,122,1342,10,21,1,83,11,So anvaḍḍhamāsaṃ ñātake sannipātetvā puttaṃ mūlasiriṃ nāma tīsu velāsu evaṃ ovadati–
589828,122,1342,22,44,1,103,14,"‘‘ idaṃ cattālīsakoṭidhanaṃ‘ bahū’’’ ti mā saññaṃ kari, vijjamānaṃ dhanaṃ na dātabbaṃ, navaṃ dhanaṃ uppādetabbaṃ. "
