589987,122,1402,2,25,1,186,22,"Tattha na taṃ kamman ti yaṃ nirayādīsu nibbattanasamatthaṃ dukkhudrayaṃ kammaṃ katvā anussaranto anussaritānussaritakkhaṇe anutappati anusocati, taṃ kataṃ na sādhu na sundaraṃ niratthakaṃ. "
589988,122,1402,26,35,1,68,8,Yassa {assumukho}ti yassa assūhi tintamukho rodanto vipākaṃ anubhotīti. 
589989,122,1403,2,12,1,99,8,"Desanāvasāne kassako upāsako sotāpattiphalaṃ patto, sampattabhikkhūpi sotāpattiphalādīni pāpuṇiṃsūti. "
589990,122,1404,2,4,1,22,2,Kassakavatthu aṭṭhamaṃ.
589991,122,1405,2,4,1,20,2,9 . Sumanamālākāravatthu 
589992,122,1406,2,17,1,110,14,Tañca kammaṃ kataṃ {sādhū}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto sumanaṃ nāma mālākāraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
589993,122,1407,2,14,1,104,11,So kira devasikaṃ bimbisārarājānaṃ pātova aṭṭhahi sumanapupphanāḷīhi upaṭṭhahanto aṭṭha kahāpaṇe labhati. 
589994,122,1407,15,32,1,190,17,Athekadivasaṃ tasmiṃ pupphāni gahetvā nagaraṃ paviṭṭhamatte bhagavā mahābhikkhusaṅghaparivuto chabbaṇṇaraṃsiyo vissajjetvā mahatā buddhānubhāvena mahatiyā buddhalīḷāya nagaraṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
589995,122,1407,33,54,1,216,20,"Bhagavā hi ekadā chabbaṇṇaraṃsiyo cīvarena paṭicchādetvā aññataro piṇḍapātiko viya carati tiṃsayojanamaggaṃ aṅgulimālassa paccuggamanaṃ gacchanto viya, ekadā chabbaṇṇaraṃsiyo vissajjetvā kapilavatthuppavesanādīsu viya. "
589996,122,1407,55,66,1,118,11,Tasmimpi divase sarīrato chabbaṇṇaraṃsiyo vissajjento mahantena buddhānubhāvena mahatiyā buddhalīḷāya rājagahaṃ pāvisi. 
589997,122,1407,67,102,1,260,26,Mālākāro bhagavato ratanagghiyasadisaṃ attabhāvaṃ disvā dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇaasītānubyañjanasarīrasobhaggaṃ oloketvā pasannacitto‘‘ kiṃ nu kho satthu adhikāraṃ karomī’’ ti cintetvā aññaṃ apassanto‘‘ imehi pupphehi bhagavantaṃ pūjessāmī’’ ti cintetvā puna cintesi–
589998,122,1407,103,129,1,137,20,"‘‘ imāni rañño nibaddhaṃ upaṭṭhānapupphāni, rājā imāni alabhanto maṃ bandhāpeyya vā ghātāpeyya vā raṭṭhato vā pabbājeyya, kiṃ nu kho karomī’’ ti? "
589999,122,1407,130,172,1,251,35,"Athassa etadahosi‘‘ rājā maṃ ghātetu vā bandhāpetu vā raṭṭhato pabbājetu vā, so hi mayhaṃ dadamānopi imasmiṃ attabhāve jīvitamattaṃ dhanaṃ dadeyya, satthupūjā pana me anekāsu kappakoṭīsu alaṃ hitāya ceva sukhāya cā’’ ti attano jīvitaṃ tathāgatassa pariccaji. "
590000,122,1408,2,23,1,114,16,"So ‘‘ yāva me pasannaṃ cittaṃ na patikuṭati, taṃ tāvadeva pūjaṃ karissāmī’’ ti haṭṭhatuṭṭho udaggudaggo satthāraṃ pūjesi. "
